WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:08.125
<i>[joyful instrumental music playing]</i>

00:30.708 --> 00:33.000
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

00:45.666 --> 00:47.666
<i>[gentle music playing]</i>

01:00.541 --> 01:02.541
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

01:22.375 --> 01:23.750
<i>[brakes squeal]</i>

01:27.250 --> 01:28.583
<i>[gasps, shivers]</i>

01:29.083 --> 01:30.458
<i>[bell clanging]</i>

01:30.541 --> 01:31.541
<i>[huffing]</i>

01:33.291 --> 01:35.291
<i>[man humming]</i>

01:39.916 --> 01:42.500
<i>-Merry Christmas.</i>
<i>-[woman] I'm working on it.</i>

01:42.583 --> 01:43.541
<i>[man] Yeah.</i>

01:43.625 --> 01:45.166
<i>[continues humming]</i>

02:03.625 --> 02:04.791
<i>[gasps]</i>

02:06.666 --> 02:07.500
<i>[sighs]</i>

02:10.625 --> 02:13.291
<i>-Absolutely not. She's awful.</i>
<i>-Uh, she's not awful.</i>

02:13.375 --> 02:15.333
<i>-She's rude.</i>
<i>-She's a little tactless.</i>

02:15.416 --> 02:16.958
<i>-And she's old.</i>
<i>-She's very, very old.</i>

02:17.041 --> 02:19.250
<i>She's the only person who could come</i>
<i>at such short notice.</i>

02:19.333 --> 02:20.791
<i>-I'm going to bed.</i>
<i>-Me too.</i>

02:20.875 --> 02:23.541
<i>-No. She'll put you to bed.</i>
<i>-That's not happening.</i>

02:23.625 --> 02:24.958
<i>We'll have nightmares.</i>

02:26.000 --> 02:28.250
<i>-You're very quiet, Mop.</i>
<i>-I already have nightmares.</i>

02:28.333 --> 02:29.708
<i>-[doorbell rings]</i>
<i>-[dog barking]</i>

02:29.791 --> 02:33.208
<i>Look, guys, guys, I'm really sorry</i>
<i>that I have to go to the office,</i>

02:33.291 --> 02:35.125
<i>but I'll be back as soon as I can.</i>

02:35.208 --> 02:37.166
<i>Your mom really loved your aunt,</i>
<i>so let's try and--</i>

02:37.250 --> 02:39.333
<i>-[doorbell ringing]</i>
<i>-[banging on door]</i>

02:42.791 --> 02:43.625
<i>Hey.</i>

02:44.125 --> 02:46.666
<i>Oh, you look awful.</i>

02:48.416 --> 02:50.791
<i>-Hello, Aunt Ruth. Good to see you too.</i>
<i>-[groans]</i>

02:50.875 --> 02:52.958
<i>-Oh, I… I don't see a tree.</i>
<i>-[door closes]</i>

02:53.583 --> 02:56.583
<i>-No decorations.</i>
<i>-No, we decided against it this year.</i>

02:56.666 --> 02:57.833
<i>That's a mistake.</i>

02:58.666 --> 03:00.333
<i>Oh, hello, children.</i>

03:01.000 --> 03:02.083
<i>How are we all?</i>

03:02.166 --> 03:05.416
<i>-They're doing great.</i>
<i>-[Aunt Ruth] Mmm. Let me look at you.</i>

03:07.375 --> 03:10.000
<i>It's as I thought, still heartbroken.</i>

03:10.083 --> 03:11.291
<i>-I'm not.</i>
<i>-Me either.</i>

03:11.375 --> 03:12.500
<i>I am.</i>

03:12.958 --> 03:16.041
<i>But I still love Mommy</i>
<i>with all the broken pieces.</i>

03:19.541 --> 03:20.666
<i>They're doing great.</i>

03:21.458 --> 03:23.000
<i>[dog whimpering]</i>

03:30.000 --> 03:34.541
<i>-You're very old.</i>
<i>-Yes. I'm very aware of it.</i>

03:35.333 --> 03:37.625
<i>I still don't get why</i>
<i>we all have to listen.</i>

03:37.708 --> 03:42.041
<i>Because the universe</i>
<i>is made of stories, not atoms.</i>

03:42.125 --> 03:46.166
<i>-That's not actually true.</i>
<i>-Well, it must be because I never lie.</i>

03:46.250 --> 03:48.416
<i>So, you listen to the story.</i>

03:48.500 --> 03:51.291
<i>After it, you sleep,</i>
<i>and then it will be Christmas.</i>

03:51.375 --> 03:53.708
<i>But we don't want it to be Christmas.</i>

03:55.125 --> 03:58.000
<i>Well, that decides the tale</i>
<i>I'm telling tonight.</i>

03:58.083 --> 04:00.291
<i>So, are you all comfortable?</i>

04:01.291 --> 04:03.958
<i>-You better be because I'm starting.</i>
<i>-[wind whooshing]</i>

04:09.750 --> 04:11.750
<i>[gentle music playing]</i>

04:14.833 --> 04:17.666
<i>[Aunt Ruth]</i> Now you may find this
hard to believe,

04:18.750 --> 04:22.833
<i>but long ago, nobody knew about Christmas.</i>

04:24.375 --> 04:28.708
<i>At this time,</i>
<i>in the middle of a forest in Finland,</i>

04:28.791 --> 04:34.125
<i>there lived an ordinary boy called Nikolas</i>
<i>along with his father,</i>

04:34.208 --> 04:39.250
<i>a humble woodcutter</i>
<i>who at the moment was quite preoccupied.</i>

04:39.333 --> 04:40.916
<i>-[bird fluttering]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

04:41.875 --> 04:43.583
<i>[quavering]</i>

04:44.416 --> 04:45.458
<i>Be the forest.</i>

04:45.541 --> 04:46.750
<i>[twigs snapping]</i>

04:47.625 --> 04:49.000
<i>[sniffing]</i>

04:49.083 --> 04:50.125
<i>[snorting]</i>

04:50.208 --> 04:51.333
<i>[growling]</i>

04:51.833 --> 04:54.250
<i>-[softly] I don't know what that means.</i>
<i>-[growling]</i>

04:54.333 --> 04:57.083
<i>-[man] It means don't move.</i>
<i>-[growling]</i>

04:58.125 --> 05:00.291
<i>When I say run, you run.</i>

05:00.791 --> 05:04.875
<i>-So stop being the forest.</i>
<i>-Yes, and run very fast.</i>

05:04.958 --> 05:06.333
<i>[snarling]</i>

05:06.916 --> 05:09.166
<i>[sniffing]</i>

05:09.250 --> 05:10.500
<i>I won't go without you.</i>

05:11.416 --> 05:13.583
<i>[snarling]</i>

05:14.625 --> 05:16.625
<i>-Then we both run!</i>
<i>-[growling]</i>

05:23.166 --> 05:24.708
<i>-[growling]</i>
<i>-[man] Come on!</i>

05:26.416 --> 05:27.583
<i>Run! Run!</i>

05:28.916 --> 05:29.875
<i>[arrow whizzing]</i>

05:31.375 --> 05:32.458
<i>[growling]</i>

05:32.541 --> 05:34.666
<i>[panting]</i>

05:34.750 --> 05:36.750
<i>[growling]</i>

05:40.791 --> 05:43.750
<i>[Aunt Ruth]</i> One crisis narrowly averted,

05:44.416 --> 05:47.958
<i>Nikolas and his father returned</i>
<i>to their cabin in the woods.</i>

05:49.916 --> 05:52.458
<i>Times were hard for father and son.</i>

05:52.541 --> 05:55.250
<i>[inhales] </i>They had barely enough
to make ends meet.

05:55.333 --> 05:57.833
<i>Wait, wait, wait. Sorry to interrupt.</i>

05:58.541 --> 05:59.541
<i>What is it?</i>

05:59.625 --> 06:00.708
<i>Where's his mommy?</i>

06:02.000 --> 06:05.208
<i>Ah, well, she died. Two years before.</i>

06:05.916 --> 06:09.166
<i>Yes, I'm afraid the bear</i>
<i>had something to do with that.</i>

06:09.250 --> 06:12.041
<i>Bear ate his mom. Got it.</i>

06:12.125 --> 06:16.333
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Well, Finland was
a very dangerous place in those days.

06:16.875 --> 06:17.708
<i>Still is.</i>

06:18.500 --> 06:20.375
<i>But despite the hardships,</i>

06:20.458 --> 06:24.875
<i>Nikolas held onto hope,</i>
<i>especially at bedtime.</i>

06:24.958 --> 06:28.083
<i>-Will you tell me the story, Papa?</i>
<i>-[Papa sighs] Not again.</i>

06:28.166 --> 06:29.250
<i>Why not?</i>

06:30.000 --> 06:31.541
<i>It isn't my story to tell.</i>

06:33.125 --> 06:34.541
<i>But Mama's not here anymore.</i>

06:36.875 --> 06:39.583
<i>Okay then, I'll tell you about Elfhelm.</i>

06:43.166 --> 06:47.125
<i>A long time ago,</i>
<i>in a place not unlike this one,</i>

06:48.125 --> 06:51.083
<i>lived a young girl named Lumi.</i>

06:52.791 --> 06:54.083
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

06:54.166 --> 06:57.375
<i>One day while gathering acorns</i>
<i>in the woods,</i>

06:58.083 --> 07:00.166
<i>Lumi became hopelessly lost.</i>

07:01.125 --> 07:02.291
<i>She tried to find her home,</i>

07:02.375 --> 07:04.833
<i>but the more she searched,</i>
<i>the farther from home she went.</i>

07:05.333 --> 07:07.916
<i>Over the river and under the moon,</i>

07:08.875 --> 07:10.833
<i>over the pointy mountain,</i>

07:10.916 --> 07:15.041
<i>all the way down past the, uh…</i>

07:15.625 --> 07:17.125
<i>[Nikolas] Past the sleeping giants.</i>

07:17.208 --> 07:20.916
<i>[Papa] Past the sleeping giants</i>
<i>and through the sky she walked.</i>

07:21.000 --> 07:25.375
<i>[inhales deeply] To a place</i>
<i>where snow was soft as clouds.</i>

07:26.791 --> 07:28.041
<i>[Nikolas] Then what happened?</i>

07:28.708 --> 07:30.416
<i>[Papa] Our Lumi was near collapse,</i>

07:30.500 --> 07:34.833
<i>and at last, she stumbled upon</i>
<i>a secret village called Elfhelm</i>

07:35.541 --> 07:38.250
<i>where lived the elves,</i>
<i>the happiest people in the world</i>

07:38.333 --> 07:40.708
<i>and the most magical place in the world.</i>

07:42.916 --> 07:45.333
<i>There Lumi stayed until the snow cleared,</i>

07:46.750 --> 07:49.958
<i>and she was finally able to return</i>
<i>to her home in the south,</i>

07:50.458 --> 07:52.041
<i>her pockets full of chocolates.</i>

07:54.416 --> 07:56.166
<i>You believe this story, don't you?</i>

07:56.250 --> 07:59.625
<i>The ending is a stretch.</i>
<i>The chocolate would have melted.</i>

08:00.250 --> 08:01.458
<i>But the rest?</i>

08:02.625 --> 08:05.291
<i>The magic and the elves?</i>

08:06.791 --> 08:08.208
<i>[Papa] I've never seen them.</i>

08:08.916 --> 08:10.333
<i>But you believe in them.</i>

08:10.916 --> 08:14.625
<i>Your mother did. And to her,</i>
<i>believing was as good as knowing.</i>

08:16.958 --> 08:18.291
<i>[mouse squeaking]</i>

08:18.375 --> 08:19.208
<i>What was that?</i>

08:19.291 --> 08:22.291
<i>-[Papa] It sounded like a squeak.</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] I think it was more of a creak.</i>

08:22.375 --> 08:24.291
<i>Definitely a squeak.</i>

08:25.083 --> 08:27.875
<i>-By the way, that's an overreaction.</i>
<i>-Out of the way, Nikolas.</i>

08:32.083 --> 08:33.833
<i>-Mouse! We have a mouse.</i>
<i>-[mouse squeaking]</i>

08:33.916 --> 08:35.708
<i>-Papa, leave him alone!</i>
<i>-[Papa grunts]</i>

08:36.250 --> 08:37.083
<i>[Nikolas] Papa.</i>

08:37.750 --> 08:39.166
<i>[Papa] He'll steal our food.</i>

08:39.250 --> 08:40.958
<i>-[Nikolas] What food?</i>
<i>-[Papa] Argh!</i>

08:41.458 --> 08:43.500
<i>[Papa] No, don't! [grunts]</i>

08:44.041 --> 08:45.916
<i>[objects clattering]</i>

08:46.000 --> 08:47.041
<i>[squeaking]</i>

08:51.750 --> 08:54.250
<i>[Papa] There he is! We've got him.</i>

08:56.333 --> 08:58.333
<i>Papa, please. Let him live.</i>

09:01.708 --> 09:02.583
<i>Please, Papa.</i>

09:03.916 --> 09:05.083
<i>[Papa grunts]</i>

09:07.833 --> 09:08.791
<i>[exhales]</i>

09:08.875 --> 09:14.625
<i>I've thought about this a lot,</i>
<i>and I've decided to call you… Miika.</i>

09:14.708 --> 09:15.541
<i>[squeaks]</i>

09:15.625 --> 09:16.708
<i>[sniffing]</i>

09:19.000 --> 09:20.916
<i>And I'm going to teach you to talk.</i>

09:21.416 --> 09:22.500
<i>[Papa scoffs]</i>

09:23.250 --> 09:25.750
<i>Boy. Boy.</i>

09:27.041 --> 09:29.875
<i>Mouse. Mouse.</i>

09:32.041 --> 09:33.041
<i>[squeaks]</i>

09:35.166 --> 09:36.625
<i>My mama always told me</i>

09:37.125 --> 09:40.500
<i>if you believe you can do something,</i>
<i>you're halfway there.</i>

09:41.458 --> 09:44.208
<i>Trees. Trees.</i>

09:44.958 --> 09:46.166
<i>-[chopping]</i>
<i>-[squeaks]</i>

09:47.083 --> 09:50.875
<i>Okay, maybe not halfway, but it's a start.</i>

09:53.916 --> 09:55.083
<i>[Papa] Ugh!</i>

09:56.625 --> 09:58.291
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>And then one day,

09:58.375 --> 10:02.083
<i>something happened</i>
<i>to light the long dark winter.</i>

10:02.666 --> 10:05.583
<i>A summons from the King himself.</i>

10:06.708 --> 10:09.208
<i>There were only two</i>
<i>of them on the invitation,</i>

10:09.291 --> 10:13.791
<i>but Nikolas saw no harm</i>
<i>in bringing along a plus one.</i>

10:13.875 --> 10:16.000
<i>We're going to see the King, Miika.</i>

10:16.666 --> 10:17.666
<i>King.</i>

10:19.208 --> 10:21.750
<i>-He's too excited to talk.</i>
<i>-He shouldn't be.</i>

10:22.791 --> 10:25.500
<i>-[bell tolling]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] Why? You love the King.</i>

10:25.583 --> 10:27.250
<i>[Papa] Of course I love the King.</i>

10:27.333 --> 10:29.958
<i>He's a great man,</i>
<i>deserves all that he has.</i>

10:30.041 --> 10:33.166
<i>The thing is, we deserve it too.</i>
<i>Everybody does.</i>

10:33.250 --> 10:36.083
<i>-[Nikolas] We manage with what we have.</i>
<i>-[sighs] We have very little.</i>

10:36.166 --> 10:37.291
<i>We have each other.</i>

10:37.375 --> 10:38.833
<i>[Papa] And that's wonderful.</i>

10:38.916 --> 10:40.541
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

10:40.625 --> 10:41.666
<i>But I want more.</i>

10:42.375 --> 10:44.375
<i>[thudding]</i>

10:44.458 --> 10:46.458
<i>[announcer] His Majesty, the King!</i>

10:47.333 --> 10:48.666
<i>[whimpering]</i>

10:58.708 --> 10:59.833
<i>[man 1 coughing]</i>

11:01.166 --> 11:04.458
<i>-Hello, everyone. Thank you for coming.</i>
<i>-[coughing continues]</i>

11:05.208 --> 11:08.291
<i>You okay? Would you like a glass of water?</i>

11:10.000 --> 11:12.500
<i>I can ring a little bell</i>
<i>and someone will bring it.</i>

11:12.583 --> 11:15.458
<i>No? Sure? All right.</i>

11:15.541 --> 11:16.708
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

11:16.791 --> 11:18.708
<i>We all know times are hard.</i>

11:18.791 --> 11:21.666
<i>I mean really, really, really hard.</i>

11:22.875 --> 11:25.583
<i>I can't remember the last time I smiled.</i>
<i>Can you?</i>

11:27.208 --> 11:28.833
<i>What is there to smile about?</i>

11:29.333 --> 11:31.041
<i>We're all miserable.</i>

11:31.958 --> 11:36.333
<i>We're all missing something,</i>
<i>and I think we know what that is.</i>

11:36.416 --> 11:40.000
<i>-A health care system.</i>
<i>-[man 2] That would be a very good thing.</i>

11:40.541 --> 11:42.250
<i>It's an idea, but not quite--</i>

11:42.333 --> 11:44.375
<i>-A living wage!</i>
<i>-[people agreeing]</i>

11:44.458 --> 11:45.708
<i>Again, worth discussing.</i>

11:45.791 --> 11:49.000
<i>A fair system of governance?</i>
<i>Enough food to feed people?</i>

11:49.083 --> 11:52.791
<i>Okay, maybe I should just tell you</i>
<i>what I think it is that we're missing.</i>

11:52.875 --> 11:54.416
<i>-[thudding]</i>
<i>-[crowd quietens]</i>

11:55.458 --> 11:58.250
<i>Hope. We all need hope.</i>

11:59.375 --> 12:03.250
<i>A spark of magic to keep us all going.</i>

12:03.958 --> 12:09.500
<i>I've gathered you here because you are</i>
<i>the hardiest men and women in the land.</i>

12:09.583 --> 12:11.041
<i>-[man 1 coughs]</i>
<i>-Not you.</i>

12:12.166 --> 12:17.083
<i>And I'm asking you</i>
<i>to go to the very edges of our kingdom.</i>

12:17.166 --> 12:18.333
<i>Go beyond</i>

12:19.541 --> 12:24.625
<i>and bring back something, anything,</i>
<i>to give us hope again.</i>

12:24.708 --> 12:25.958
<i>-[man 3] A visionist.</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

12:26.541 --> 12:30.625
<i>[King] The eyes of our great nation</i>
<i>will be on this quest.</i>

12:31.375 --> 12:32.416
<i>[Nikolas whispering] Oh no.</i>

12:32.500 --> 12:35.416
<i>Any who set out</i>
<i>will be well paid for their efforts.</i>

12:35.500 --> 12:38.416
<i>-[squeaking]</i>
<i>-The path may be dangerous.</i>

12:38.500 --> 12:41.583
<i>Some of you will die,</i>
<i>probably most of you.</i>

12:42.083 --> 12:45.625
<i>But if you succeed,</i>
<i>your award will be far greater.</i>

12:45.708 --> 12:47.250
<i>-Got you, Miika!</i>
<i>-[man 4] Say what?</i>

12:48.416 --> 12:49.416
<i>[King] Seize him!</i>

12:50.500 --> 12:51.458
<i>[gasps]</i>

12:53.666 --> 12:56.541
<i>-Forgive him, sire. I beg of you.</i>
<i>-[people murmuring]</i>

12:58.000 --> 13:01.708
<i>I'm so sorry, Your Majesty.</i>
<i>He lives in the clouds, this one.</i>

13:02.208 --> 13:04.583
<i>-[weapons swishing]</i>
<i>-Lucky boy.</i>

13:05.416 --> 13:06.500
<i>[coin clinks]</i>

13:07.833 --> 13:08.833
<i>What'd he give you?</i>

13:08.916 --> 13:11.750
<i>Two kind words, Papa,</i>
<i>that'll warm me through the long month.</i>

13:11.833 --> 13:13.375
<i>[Papa] No, how much money?</i>

13:14.041 --> 13:14.875
<i>I don't know.</i>

13:15.458 --> 13:18.416
<i>This is half a crown.</i>
<i>Can feed a mouse for a week with this.</i>

13:18.500 --> 13:19.708
<i>[Nikolas chuckles]</i>

13:21.416 --> 13:22.250
<i>[Nikolas] Fork.</i>

13:23.958 --> 13:24.791
<i>Pine cone.</i>

13:26.041 --> 13:26.875
<i>Spoon.</i>

13:29.125 --> 13:31.750
<i>Please say something, Miika. Anything.</i>

13:33.625 --> 13:34.708
<i>[banging on door]</i>

13:40.916 --> 13:42.916
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

13:43.916 --> 13:44.750
<i>Anders?</i>

13:46.958 --> 13:49.833
<i>Yes, it is me.</i>

13:51.375 --> 13:54.041
<i>Pretty close thing with the bear</i>
<i>the other day. Thank you for that.</i>

13:54.125 --> 13:56.750
<i>We need to talk.</i>
<i>Can the boy go to another room?</i>

14:00.000 --> 14:02.916
<i>-We don't have another room.</i>
<i>-And I want to hear.</i>

14:03.000 --> 14:06.083
<i>We can talk outside.</i>
<i>You're welcome to borrow my hat.</i>

14:06.583 --> 14:07.583
<i>I'll survive.</i>

14:10.833 --> 14:12.541
<i>What do you think that's all about, Miika?</i>

14:12.625 --> 14:13.958
<i>-[sniffing]</i>
<i>-[door closes]</i>

14:17.333 --> 14:19.333
<i>[indistinct conversation]</i>

14:26.166 --> 14:28.125
<i>[Nikolas grunting]</i>

14:30.000 --> 14:35.125
<i>Nikolas, the King's quest,</i>
<i>I'm going to do it.</i>

14:36.041 --> 14:37.416
<i>You're going away?</i>

14:37.500 --> 14:40.250
<i>Not for long. Two months.</i>

14:40.333 --> 14:41.625
<i>Two months?</i>

14:41.708 --> 14:44.875
<i>Maybe three.</i>
<i>But I'll be back before you know it.</i>

14:45.541 --> 14:48.541
<i>-It'll be worth it.</i>
<i>-To bring some new hope to the world?</i>

14:49.041 --> 14:50.750
<i>To claim the reward.</i>

14:50.833 --> 14:53.416
<i>But isn't the reward</i>
<i>bringing us new hope and wonder?</i>

14:54.333 --> 14:55.750
<i>The reward is the money,</i>

14:57.208 --> 15:01.583
<i>and the money means food and warm clothes</i>
<i>so you can have a life.</i>

15:03.375 --> 15:05.541
<i>The life</i>
<i>I stood at your mother's grave site</i>

15:05.625 --> 15:07.000
<i>and promised you'd have.</i>

15:08.166 --> 15:09.708
<i>Nikolas, please.</i>

15:11.250 --> 15:12.250
<i>Nikolas!</i>

15:16.833 --> 15:18.958
<i>[breathes deeply]</i>

15:19.041 --> 15:20.041
<i>[sniffles]</i>

15:20.125 --> 15:22.125
<i>[fire crackling]</i>

15:29.416 --> 15:30.666
<i>[Nikolas] Where will you go?</i>

15:31.666 --> 15:33.375
<i>Anders is assembling a group.</i>

15:34.458 --> 15:38.541
<i>We'll be heading north,</i>
<i>far north, to find Elfhelm.</i>

15:38.625 --> 15:40.125
<i>-Elfhelm!</i>
<i>-[Papa] If it exists.</i>

15:40.208 --> 15:42.958
<i>-I know it does. You have to take me.</i>
<i>-[Papa] No, it's too dangerous.</i>

15:43.041 --> 15:44.625
<i>There'll be many nights sleeping out</i>
<i>in the cold.</i>

15:44.708 --> 15:46.041
<i>That's fine. I love the cold.</i>

15:46.125 --> 15:47.500
<i>Once you get north of Seipajarvi,</i>

15:47.583 --> 15:50.333
<i>there's nothing but ice planes and lakes</i>
<i>and snow-covered fields.</i>

15:50.416 --> 15:51.833
<i>Snow-covered fields are my favorite.</i>

15:51.916 --> 15:53.500
<i>After that, the journey only gets harder,</i>

15:53.583 --> 15:55.375
<i>which is why no one's made it</i>
<i>to the far north.</i>

15:55.458 --> 15:57.833
<i>That's not why.</i>
<i>It's because no one knows the way.</i>

15:57.916 --> 16:01.291
<i>The words in the story are totally vague,</i>
<i>and you can barely remember them anyway.</i>

16:01.875 --> 16:04.208
<i>Please, Papa. I can help. I know I can.</i>

16:05.375 --> 16:06.375
<i>Please.</i>

16:09.083 --> 16:10.583
<i>I set off at first light.</i>

16:19.375 --> 16:20.500
<i>[sighs]</i>

16:21.541 --> 16:23.041
<i>I'll miss you, Christmas.</i>

16:29.625 --> 16:32.125
<i>You never told me why Mama called me that.</i>

16:34.666 --> 16:36.166
<i>She never told me either.</i>

16:37.666 --> 16:40.625
<i>It's just a word.</i>
<i>It doesn't have to mean anything.</i>

16:42.875 --> 16:46.291
<i>[woman]</i> Dearest brother,
thank you for the generous offer

16:46.375 --> 16:49.375
<i>of allowing me to look after the child.</i>

16:50.500 --> 16:51.750
<i>Who's gonna look after me?</i>

16:51.833 --> 16:57.625
<i>[woman] </i>Oh, the pure joy of spending time
with my nephew is all the payment I need.

16:57.708 --> 17:02.000
<i>[chuckles] </i>Although, if you insist,
I'm sure we can come to an understanding.

17:02.083 --> 17:03.916
<i>Don't worry. I've written to my sister.</i>

17:04.000 --> 17:07.000
<i>-[woman grunting]</i>
<i>-</i>Signed, your doting sister.

17:07.875 --> 17:08.958
<i>Not Aunt Carlotta.</i>

17:09.041 --> 17:10.000
<i>[knocking on door]</i>

17:10.083 --> 17:12.541
<i>Would you deny your aunt the pleasure?</i>
<i>She's a lonely woman.</i>

17:12.625 --> 17:14.333
<i>-I wonder why.</i>
<i>-Shh.</i>

17:15.583 --> 17:17.041
<i>[door creaking]</i>

17:17.125 --> 17:18.166
<i>[panting] Brother!</i>

17:18.250 --> 17:20.958
<i>Oh… [panting]</i>

17:21.041 --> 17:24.000
<i>How happy I was</i>
<i>to get your message. [chuckles]</i>

17:24.083 --> 17:25.458
<i>I knew you would be.</i>

17:25.541 --> 17:31.166
<i>And, oh, what a lovely long walk I had</i>
<i>to get here.</i>

17:31.250 --> 17:35.583
<i>How clever of you to have built</i>
<i>this hut at the actual end of the world.</i>

17:35.666 --> 17:39.416
<i>Nikolas, oh, it's delightful to see you.</i>

17:39.500 --> 17:40.416
<i>[bag thuds on floor]</i>

17:41.125 --> 17:42.791
<i>And you, Aunt Carlotta.</i>

17:43.291 --> 17:45.333
<i>Oh, Auntie, please.</i>

17:45.416 --> 17:47.541
<i>[chuckles] We're a happy family.</i>

17:48.375 --> 17:49.916
<i>[squeaking, sniffing]</i>

17:51.666 --> 17:53.375
<i>[dogs barking]</i>

17:53.875 --> 17:55.500
<i>[Anders] Hurry up, man. Load up.</i>

17:56.291 --> 17:58.916
<i>Say your goodbyes, woodcutter.</i>

18:00.083 --> 18:01.916
<i>[men speaking indistinctly]</i>

18:04.416 --> 18:05.916
<i>I'll make this worth it.</i>

18:06.958 --> 18:08.000
<i>Nothing could be.</i>

18:09.625 --> 18:10.708
<i>[sobbing]</i>

18:11.750 --> 18:13.708
<i>Woodcutter, it's time.</i>

18:14.583 --> 18:15.541
<i>Papa.</i>

18:16.666 --> 18:17.666
<i>Papa.</i>

18:18.208 --> 18:20.125
<i>Okay. I'm ready.</i>

18:21.750 --> 18:22.750
<i>Papa, wait.</i>

18:24.583 --> 18:26.041
<i>-Your knife.</i>
<i>-[Papa] Ah.</i>

18:28.166 --> 18:29.250
<i>You have this.</i>

18:29.333 --> 18:30.791
<i>Mama made it for you.</i>

18:31.291 --> 18:33.250
<i>She said I might need it one day.</i>

18:33.833 --> 18:37.125
<i>Now I need you to be warm and safe.</i>

18:37.958 --> 18:40.000
<i>-And blind?</i>
<i>-[both chuckle]</i>

18:43.458 --> 18:44.458
<i>I love you.</i>

18:45.291 --> 18:46.875
<i>-[Anders yells]</i>
<i>-[dogs barking]</i>

18:46.958 --> 18:48.958
<i>[ululating]</i>

18:51.666 --> 18:53.666
<i>[Anders yelling]</i>

18:56.416 --> 18:57.458
<i>[sighs]</i>

18:57.541 --> 18:59.750
<i>Finally. What a racket.</i>

19:03.375 --> 19:04.666
<i>Now…</i>

19:06.166 --> 19:07.583
<i>it's just the two of us.</i>

19:09.041 --> 19:11.416
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Aunt Carlotta
had turned into exactly--

19:11.500 --> 19:12.333
<i>[girl]</i> Stop again.

19:13.125 --> 19:13.958
<i>Yes?</i>

19:14.041 --> 19:16.541
<i>-Will he ever see his dad again?</i>
<i>-[Aunt Ruth] Yes.</i>

19:16.625 --> 19:17.458
<i>You promise?</i>

19:17.958 --> 19:19.916
<i>I never lie. Can I go on?</i>

19:20.000 --> 19:20.916
<i>You better.</i>

19:21.000 --> 19:21.875
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

19:21.958 --> 19:28.333
<i>Right. Aunt Carlotta had turned into</i>
<i>exactly what Nikolas had been dreading.</i>

19:29.041 --> 19:33.041
<i>Out! Move it! Monster, go.</i>

19:33.125 --> 19:36.666
<i>The first rule is you can't sleep in here.</i>
<i>I need my privacy.</i>

19:36.750 --> 19:38.833
<i>-It's so cold out--</i>
<i>-Don't talk back to me.</i>

19:38.916 --> 19:40.333
<i>-I'm not talking--</i>
<i>-Don't talk back!</i>

19:40.416 --> 19:42.083
<i>-It's cold out.</i>
<i>-You're doing it now.</i>

19:42.583 --> 19:44.375
<i>The second rule is…</i>

19:44.458 --> 19:46.208
<i>no rats.</i>

19:46.291 --> 19:48.250
<i>[Nikolas] But he's not a rat.</i>
<i>He's a mouse.</i>

19:48.333 --> 19:51.916
<i>[Aunt Carlotta] He is</i>
<i>a disgusting miniature rat!</i>

19:52.000 --> 19:55.750
<i>-[Nikolas] Leave him alone!</i>
<i>-Oh! Oh, you dirty little beast!</i>

19:55.833 --> 19:57.750
<i>-Miika! No, Miika!</i>
<i>-[squeaking]</i>

19:57.833 --> 20:01.708
<i>And no horrible,</i>
<i>rotten vegetables either! Ugh!</i>

20:01.791 --> 20:03.125
<i>[Nikolas] My turnip doll!</i>

20:03.208 --> 20:04.708
<i>My mama made that for me.</i>

20:04.791 --> 20:06.875
<i>Look, he's got a face.</i>

20:07.958 --> 20:12.583
<i>Oh, look, it's got a face. Ugh.</i>
<i>I've forgotten how much I hate children.</i>

20:12.666 --> 20:13.958
<i>-[footsteps receding]</i>
<i>-[squeaking]</i>

20:14.875 --> 20:16.166
<i>-[grunts angrily]</i>
<i>-[door slams]</i>

20:17.083 --> 20:19.083
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

20:23.833 --> 20:25.250
<i>[water flowing]</i>

20:25.333 --> 20:26.666
<i>[owl hooting]</i>

20:27.208 --> 20:29.208
<i>[gentle music playing]</i>

20:35.166 --> 20:36.375
<i>[exhales]</i>

20:41.166 --> 20:44.375
<i>You see that, Miika?</i>
<i>It means you have to make a wish.</i>

20:45.750 --> 20:49.666
<i>I wish that my father succeeds,</i>
<i>brings back something magic.</i>

20:52.958 --> 20:53.958
<i>We all need it.</i>

20:54.625 --> 20:56.625
<i>[yawning]</i>

20:56.708 --> 20:58.708
<i>[shivering]</i>

20:58.791 --> 20:59.750
<i>[owl hooting]</i>

20:59.833 --> 21:02.541
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Time is slow
for those who wait.

21:04.833 --> 21:08.250
<i>And as Nikolas waited, he grew thin.</i>

21:08.750 --> 21:10.416
<i>[stomach rumbling]</i>

21:12.625 --> 21:14.833
<i>Is that you making</i>
<i>that awful rumbling sound.</i>

21:14.916 --> 21:16.583
<i>It's my tummy, Aunt Carlotta.</i>

21:16.666 --> 21:19.458
<i>Oh, stop complaining.</i>
<i>I'm hungrier than you are.</i>

21:19.958 --> 21:22.416
<i>-You're eating my breakfast.</i>
<i>-I'm not enjoying it.</i>

21:22.500 --> 21:24.041
<i>Even snow has more taste.</i>

21:25.958 --> 21:29.708
<i>Why can't you have nice things</i>
<i>in your house like marzipan or cake?</i>

21:31.750 --> 21:32.750
<i>Chocolate.</i>

21:32.833 --> 21:34.291
<i>[breathes deeply]</i>

21:34.375 --> 21:36.125
<i>Why can't I have a chocolate?</i>

21:36.208 --> 21:38.500
<i>Because these things</i>
<i>don't just appear magically.</i>

21:38.583 --> 21:39.791
<i>[bowl clatters]</i>

21:43.041 --> 21:45.458
<i>Well, wouldn't life be nicer if they did?</i>

21:49.458 --> 21:51.958
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Home is not a place.

21:52.041 --> 21:53.416
<i>It's a feeling.</i>

21:54.125 --> 21:59.041
<i>And as the days stretched into weeks</i>
<i>and his father did not return,</i>

21:59.541 --> 22:03.083
<i>Nikolas started to wonder</i>
<i>if he'd ever feel it again.</i>

22:03.166 --> 22:05.166
<i>[Aunt Carlotta humming]</i>

22:06.625 --> 22:09.041
<i>Oh, Nikolas.</i>

22:09.958 --> 22:12.041
<i>There you are. [grunts]</i>

22:13.458 --> 22:17.666
<i>I have… ooh, made you some soup.</i>

22:18.916 --> 22:20.458
<i>-You have?</i>
<i>-Mm-hmm.</i>

22:28.500 --> 22:29.541
<i>What's it made with?</i>

22:31.916 --> 22:32.750
<i>Love.</i>

22:43.208 --> 22:44.250
<i>[blowing]</i>

22:44.833 --> 22:46.791
<i>[slurping, gulping]</i>

22:48.583 --> 22:49.708
<i>[slurping] Mmm.</i>

22:51.083 --> 22:54.166
<i>-Yes, that's it.</i>
<i>-[slurping] Mmm. Mmm.</i>

22:54.250 --> 22:55.833
<i>Eat up. [grunts]</i>

22:57.583 --> 22:59.500
<i>-[sizzling]</i>
<i>-[Aunt Carlotta] Ouch!</i>

22:59.583 --> 23:00.458
<i>[sighs]</i>

23:00.541 --> 23:03.833
<i>-I should never have come here.</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] You can always go home.</i>

23:04.333 --> 23:07.125
<i>I've got Miika</i>
<i>and the turnip doll Mama made me.</i>

23:08.083 --> 23:09.125
<i>[slurping]</i>

23:09.708 --> 23:10.708
<i>So I'll be fine.</i>

23:12.416 --> 23:17.875
<i>Funny you should mention that thing.</i>

23:20.750 --> 23:22.000
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

23:25.041 --> 23:25.916
<i>[gasps]</i>

23:29.958 --> 23:30.916
<i>[laughs]</i>

23:35.125 --> 23:38.083
<i>-No! How could you do that?</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

23:38.166 --> 23:42.166
<i>Oh, you're such a sentimental fool.</i>
<i>Just like your mother was.</i>

23:42.250 --> 23:46.458
<i>Don't you dare speak about her like that!</i>
<i>She was kind and caring--</i>

23:46.541 --> 23:50.583
<i>And foolish! Just like your father,</i>
<i>running through the woods chasing stories,</i>

23:50.666 --> 23:52.541
<i>which will surely get him killed too.</i>

23:53.208 --> 23:55.958
<i>Everyone knows</i>
<i>there is no such thing as elves.</i>

23:56.041 --> 23:57.291
<i>That's not true.</i>

23:57.375 --> 24:01.416
<i>And there is no such place as Elfhelm.</i>

24:02.041 --> 24:03.166
<i>[sniffing]</i>

24:05.083 --> 24:06.166
<i>-[Aunt Carlotta screams]</i>
<i>-No!</i>

24:06.250 --> 24:08.083
<i>[Aunt Carlotta] Get that thing</i>
<i>out of the house!</i>

24:08.166 --> 24:10.291
<i>-No!</i>
<i>-[Aunt Carlotta] You little brat!</i>

24:11.875 --> 24:13.333
<i>[hissing]</i>

24:16.250 --> 24:17.166
<i>It's ruined.</i>

24:19.875 --> 24:21.208
<i>[gasps]</i>

24:29.291 --> 24:30.500
<i>[grunts]</i>

24:38.625 --> 24:39.833
<i>Over the river,</i>

24:40.875 --> 24:41.833
<i>under the moon,</i>

24:42.958 --> 24:44.333
<i>up the pointy mountain,</i>

24:45.625 --> 24:47.125
<i>past the sleeping giants…</i>

24:51.208 --> 24:53.125
<i>Elfhelm. [exhales sharply]</i>

24:58.666 --> 25:02.958
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>And just like that,
Nikolas had a purpose.

25:04.333 --> 25:05.250
<i>A mission.</i>

25:05.333 --> 25:07.333
<i>[gentle music playing]</i>

25:08.666 --> 25:09.666
<i>[chuckles softly]</i>

25:15.916 --> 25:17.750
<i>[snoring]</i>

25:26.625 --> 25:28.666
<i>-[squeaking]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas sighs]</i>

25:30.666 --> 25:33.875
<i>I'm going to find my father, Miika,</i>
<i>and give him the map.</i>

25:34.500 --> 25:37.041
<i>But it's a long and dangerous journey</i>
<i>to the far north</i>

25:37.125 --> 25:38.708
<i>with a high risk of death.</i>

25:40.000 --> 25:41.375
<i>You don't have to come.</i>

25:43.541 --> 25:44.500
<i>[squeaking]</i>

25:50.000 --> 25:52.166
<i>[sniffing]</i>

25:52.250 --> 25:55.333
<i>Sometimes I'm glad</i>
<i>you don't understand a word I say.</i>

25:57.291 --> 26:00.583
<i>-Trees. Trees.</i>
<i>-[birds chirping]</i>

26:01.125 --> 26:03.833
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>And so the two friends
began their journey…

26:03.916 --> 26:04.916
<i>[Nikolas] Trees.</i>

26:05.000 --> 26:09.375
<i>…away from misery</i>
<i>and towards the great unknown.</i>

26:10.375 --> 26:12.041
<i>The far north.</i>

26:12.125 --> 26:14.958
<i>[pleasant orchestral music playing]</i>

26:26.500 --> 26:28.541
<i>[music continues]</i>

26:46.833 --> 26:48.833
<i>[snorting]</i>

26:49.958 --> 26:51.958
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

26:54.166 --> 26:55.250
<i>[woman] Hey, boy.</i>

26:58.291 --> 26:59.333
<i>[goose honking]</i>

26:59.416 --> 27:00.375
<i>Good morning.</i>

27:01.083 --> 27:04.500
<i>Where go you, mysterious boy</i>
<i>with a mouse on your shoulder?</i>

27:04.583 --> 27:06.166
<i>I'm going to help my father.</i>

27:06.250 --> 27:08.458
<i>He's part of an expedition</i>
<i>to the far north.</i>

27:08.541 --> 27:11.833
<i>You're too small</i>
<i>to help anybody, little boy.</i>

27:12.333 --> 27:14.666
<i>And the far north is a dangerous place.</i>

27:14.750 --> 27:18.083
<i>-No, they've gone to find Elfhelm.</i>
<i>-[spits]</i>

27:20.458 --> 27:24.916
<i>Never believe anything,</i>
<i>especially fairy tales</i>

27:25.000 --> 27:29.041
<i>about magical towns</i>
<i>with tiny, happy people.</i>

27:29.125 --> 27:29.958
<i>[squeaks]</i>

27:30.041 --> 27:33.041
<i>Fall off a bridge, boy. It'll hurt less.</i>

27:33.916 --> 27:35.625
<i>[laughs hysterically]</i>

27:41.125 --> 27:43.125
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

27:48.125 --> 27:52.375
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>With just the map
to guide him, Nikolas plowed on.

27:56.625 --> 27:58.958
<i>Cold and hungry.</i>

27:59.041 --> 28:00.583
<i>[wind whistling]</i>

28:00.666 --> 28:05.125
<i>The words of the old woman ringing</i>
<i>in his ears.</i>

28:05.208 --> 28:07.000
<i>She's wrong, isn't she, Miika?</i>

28:08.625 --> 28:11.166
<i>We'll find him. I know we will.</i>

28:12.208 --> 28:14.125
<i>We just… [exhales]</i>

28:16.333 --> 28:17.750
<i>We just have to get there.</i>

28:21.916 --> 28:22.916
<i>This way.</i>

28:29.333 --> 28:31.333
<i>[wind howling]</i>

28:35.666 --> 28:36.666
<i>[flint striking]</i>

28:38.958 --> 28:40.458
<i>-[Nikolas grunts]</i>
<i>-[flint striking]</i>

28:44.083 --> 28:45.416
<i>[fire crackling]</i>

28:52.000 --> 28:53.416
<i>Do you believe in magic, Miika?</i>

28:56.208 --> 28:58.375
<i>Because I don't think I do anymore.</i>

29:00.041 --> 29:00.875
<i>[scoffs]</i>

29:00.958 --> 29:05.708
<i>If there was a time where you could prove</i>
<i>that magic was true and real and amazing,</i>

29:06.541 --> 29:07.916
<i>it would be this one.</i>

29:09.458 --> 29:11.333
<i>[grunts, squeaks]</i>

29:12.166 --> 29:13.000
<i>Boy.</i>

29:15.083 --> 29:18.833
<i>Mouse. Tree. Ball. Spoon. Huh.</i>

29:18.916 --> 29:21.291
<i>Miika, you can talk.</i>

29:21.375 --> 29:24.083
<i>Yeah, of course, I can talk.</i>
<i>And I can fly as well.</i>

29:24.750 --> 29:26.125
<i>No, just kidding. No mice can fly.</i>

29:26.208 --> 29:28.708
<i>-That'd be absurd.</i>
<i>-Why didn't you speak before?</i>

29:28.791 --> 29:30.833
<i>I was waiting</i>
<i>until I could form a proper sentence,</i>

29:30.916 --> 29:34.958
<i>which, with your one word at a time</i>
<i>teaching system, did take forever.</i>

29:35.041 --> 29:38.416
<i>So, um, can we talk about</i>
<i>something very important?</i>

29:38.500 --> 29:40.083
<i>-What's that?</i>
<i>-Cheese.</i>

29:41.583 --> 29:42.791
<i>Does it exist?</i>

29:43.791 --> 29:47.125
<i>I've never seen any.</i>
<i>That doesn't mean I don't believe in it.</i>

29:47.208 --> 29:50.208
<i>Well, I'd rather taste it</i>
<i>than just believe in it. But, uh…</i>

29:53.375 --> 29:54.958
<i>This is what you call a fire, is it?</i>

29:58.416 --> 29:59.416
<i>[Miika] Trees.</i>

30:00.166 --> 30:03.875
<i>We are walking…</i>
<i>We are walking among the snowy trees.</i>

30:03.958 --> 30:05.000
<i>[Miika chuckles]</i>

30:05.541 --> 30:07.291
<i>What's that? Oh, look, squirrel.</i>

30:08.041 --> 30:09.708
<i>Dead, frozen squirrel.</i>

30:10.416 --> 30:13.125
<i>Strange word, isn't it? Squirrel.</i>

30:13.208 --> 30:15.083
<i>Hello, I'm a little squirrel.</i>

30:15.791 --> 30:17.500
<i>[Miika sniffing]</i>

30:19.000 --> 30:23.000
<i>What's the word</i>
<i>for, um, the really scary big thing</i>

30:23.083 --> 30:25.541
<i>that has four legs</i>
<i>and sort of horns on its head?</i>

30:25.625 --> 30:28.958
<i>-What's that… What's that word?</i>
<i>-I don't know. Reindeer?</i>

30:29.041 --> 30:31.583
<i>-That's it. Yeah, a reindeer.</i>
<i>-Why'd you ask?</i>

30:31.666 --> 30:34.166
<i>Oh, no reason except</i>
<i>one's charging straight at us!</i>

30:34.250 --> 30:35.833
<i>-[hoofs thundering]</i>
<i>-[huffs]</i>

30:35.916 --> 30:37.375
<i>-[Nikolas screams]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

30:39.041 --> 30:40.000
<i>[grunts]</i>

30:40.083 --> 30:42.791
<i>-[Miika] Pick me up! Go, go, go!</i>
<i>-[grunting]</i>

30:42.875 --> 30:44.458
<i>[Nikolas panting]</i>

30:45.250 --> 30:46.208
<i>[huffs]</i>

30:49.000 --> 30:50.000
<i>[grunting]</i>

30:53.875 --> 30:56.375
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[panting, grunting]</i>

30:59.625 --> 31:00.666
<i>[bellows]</i>

31:00.750 --> 31:01.750
<i>Hold on, Miika.</i>

31:02.250 --> 31:03.916
<i>[grunting]</i>

31:04.000 --> 31:05.250
<i>[bellows]</i>

31:06.625 --> 31:09.125
<i>[bellows ferociously]</i>

31:09.958 --> 31:10.916
<i>[Nikolas yells]</i>

31:12.500 --> 31:13.916
<i>[grunting]</i>

31:16.083 --> 31:17.583
<i>[grunts, snorts]</i>

31:19.458 --> 31:21.041
<i>-I think he's hurt.</i>
<i>-[Miika] So?</i>

31:21.666 --> 31:23.541
<i>[snorts, groans]</i>

31:24.083 --> 31:25.791
<i>Look, an arrow.</i>

31:25.875 --> 31:28.958
<i>Ignore it. I'm pretty sure</i>
<i>it will just fall out on its own.</i>

31:29.541 --> 31:33.291
<i>-Just leave it. It's not our problem.</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] I can't do that. [grunts]</i>

31:35.125 --> 31:36.625
<i>-[Miika] Now it's our problem.</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

31:36.708 --> 31:37.958
<i>Whoa, whoa, whoa.</i>

31:38.958 --> 31:41.416
<i>-Calm down, boy. It's all right.</i>
<i>-[grunts, snorts]</i>

31:42.625 --> 31:44.041
<i>[grunts, huffs]</i>

31:44.583 --> 31:45.416
<i>See?</i>

31:46.166 --> 31:47.750
<i>[grunting, snorting]</i>

31:48.291 --> 31:49.791
<i>-[huffs]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

31:50.375 --> 31:52.541
<i>[chuffing]</i>

31:57.583 --> 32:01.333
<i>Okay, I'm not gonna hurt you. Okay?</i>

32:03.416 --> 32:05.166
<i>-Touch his face, yeah?</i>
<i>-Don't worry.</i>

32:05.250 --> 32:07.083
<i>-[snorts]</i>
<i>-Shh.</i>

32:09.833 --> 32:12.875
<i>-[reindeer grunts]</i>
<i>-Anders, the hunter.</i>

32:15.500 --> 32:17.791
<i>[grunting]</i>

32:22.125 --> 32:23.166
<i>[Nikolas grunts]</i>

32:24.333 --> 32:26.500
<i>You ready? On three.</i>

32:27.750 --> 32:28.833
<i>[huffs]</i>

32:28.916 --> 32:31.333
<i>One, two… [grunts]</i>

32:31.416 --> 32:34.125
<i>[bellows]</i>

32:38.375 --> 32:41.000
<i>Don't worry. It's all right. It's okay.</i>

32:41.625 --> 32:44.583
<i>See? Nothing to worry about. [grunts]</i>

32:45.750 --> 32:47.541
<i>[panting]</i>

32:47.625 --> 32:48.708
<i>[huffs]</i>

32:54.583 --> 32:56.125
<i>[bellows]</i>

32:57.333 --> 32:59.458
<i>Good boy. Have a nice day.</i>

33:00.125 --> 33:01.208
<i>[Miika] Cheers, mate.</i>

33:01.958 --> 33:04.083
<i>Well, that went</i>
<i>a lot better than expected.</i>

33:04.166 --> 33:05.750
<i>Given I thought we were both gonna die.</i>

33:07.916 --> 33:09.625
<i>[grunts gently, huffs]</i>

33:09.708 --> 33:11.791
<i>[sweeping orchestral music playing]</i>

33:31.125 --> 33:33.541
<i>[reindeer chuffing]</i>

33:37.708 --> 33:39.125
<i>[hoofs treading]</i>

33:40.291 --> 33:41.250
<i>[Nikolas] Shoo!</i>

33:42.208 --> 33:45.875
<i>You don't want to come with us.</i>
<i>We have a long way still to go.</i>

33:53.083 --> 33:55.083
<i>[chuffing]</i>

33:55.166 --> 33:56.666
<i>[grunting]</i>

33:59.375 --> 34:01.583
<i>-You want me to climb on your back?</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

34:03.375 --> 34:06.250
<i>-Sorry, what's happening?</i>
<i>-Is that a "yes" in reindeer?</i>

34:06.333 --> 34:09.958
<i>-Let's go with no. How about that?</i>
<i>-I don't think we have a choice.</i>

34:10.041 --> 34:12.708
<i>Why teach me to talk</i>
<i>if you're never gonna listen?</i>

34:12.791 --> 34:15.375
<i>Don't. Definitely no…</i>
<i>Okay, we're climbing on.</i>

34:18.208 --> 34:19.208
<i>Whoa!</i>

34:19.291 --> 34:21.291
<i>[adventurous music playing]</i>

34:37.291 --> 34:39.291
<i>[screams]</i>

34:41.083 --> 34:42.083
<i>[reindeer bellows]</i>

34:46.833 --> 34:47.958
<i>[Nikolas] Look, Miika!</i>

34:48.833 --> 34:50.666
<i>The very pointy mountain.</i>

34:50.750 --> 34:52.125
<i>We're nearly there.</i>

34:55.208 --> 34:56.458
<i>[wind whistling]</i>

34:57.666 --> 35:01.250
<i>[Nikolas] I can't just call you reindeer.</i>
<i>I'll pick a name for you.</i>

35:01.333 --> 35:04.041
<i>Oh, bad idea.</i>
<i>That's how I ended up with Miika.</i>

35:05.375 --> 35:09.458
<i>When I was young, I used to go sledding</i>
<i>with my mom around Lake Blitzen.</i>

35:10.041 --> 35:11.416
<i>How about that for a name?</i>

35:11.500 --> 35:14.125
<i>[Miika] Which one?</i>
<i>Lake or Blitzen? Or… Or both?</i>

35:14.208 --> 35:17.333
<i>Do you mean both?</i>
<i>That seems a bit much to me.</i>

35:18.041 --> 35:20.208
<i>Onward, my faithful reindeer,</i>
<i>Lake Blitzen.</i>

35:20.291 --> 35:21.583
<i>-Miika.</i>
<i>-[Miika] Huh?</i>

35:21.666 --> 35:22.500
<i>[Nikolas] Look.</i>

35:23.500 --> 35:24.833
<i>[sniffing]</i>

35:25.583 --> 35:26.875
<i>Sleeping giants.</i>

35:32.958 --> 35:35.375
<i>-We're getting close.</i>
<i>-To what?</i>

35:37.083 --> 35:38.083
<i>[Nikolas] Elfhelm.</i>

35:39.541 --> 35:40.541
<i>My father.</i>

35:40.625 --> 35:42.625
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

35:44.916 --> 35:46.916
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

35:47.958 --> 35:50.458
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>But on the other side
of the mountain,

35:51.375 --> 35:55.416
<i>they found only snow and more snow.</i>

35:57.166 --> 36:00.250
<i>Elfhelm was nowhere in sight.</i>

36:00.916 --> 36:02.250
<i>[Nikolas] I don't understand.</i>

36:02.958 --> 36:06.083
<i>We must have made a wrong turn.</i>
<i>There's nothing here.</i>

36:08.083 --> 36:09.166
<i>[Miika] Nothing here.</i>

36:09.833 --> 36:13.166
<i>What do you mean nothing here?</i>
<i>Wasn't this the plan?</i>

36:14.250 --> 36:17.208
<i>What are we gonna do, Nikolas? Wait.</i>

36:19.000 --> 36:20.000
<i>Wait.</i>

36:20.833 --> 36:23.750
<i>Nikolas, what are we gonna do?</i>

36:27.500 --> 36:29.458
<i>-Blitzen, over there!</i>
<i>-[Blitzen grunts]</i>

36:30.708 --> 36:33.791
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>And then
things took a turn for the worse.

36:33.875 --> 36:35.875
<i>-[Blitzen grunting]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas panting]</i>

36:41.916 --> 36:43.208
<i>[panting]</i>

36:45.208 --> 36:46.041
<i>Papa.</i>

36:47.458 --> 36:49.916
<i>Is… Is that his knife?</i>

36:50.708 --> 36:53.583
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Nikolas felt doubt
weighing him down.

36:53.666 --> 36:54.583
<i>Papa.</i>

36:54.666 --> 36:57.000
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>The quest out of reach.

36:57.083 --> 36:58.708
<i>Nikolas, what's wrong?</i>

36:58.791 --> 37:01.625
<i>I tried to find him, Miika,</i>
<i>but I couldn't.</i>

37:02.166 --> 37:03.333
<i>[sobbing]</i>

37:03.416 --> 37:05.333
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>The temperature plummeted.

37:05.416 --> 37:06.750
<i>I'm so tired.</i>

37:06.833 --> 37:09.416
<i>[Aunt Ruth]</i>
The air itself began to freeze.

37:09.500 --> 37:10.333
<i>[Miika] Nikolas.</i>

37:10.416 --> 37:13.000
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Nikolas's heartbeat slowed,

37:14.125 --> 37:16.750
<i>each breath an effort.</i>

37:16.833 --> 37:18.083
<i>[Miika] Nikolas.</i>

37:18.166 --> 37:20.333
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>He had done
everything he could.

37:21.375 --> 37:23.041
<i>But it wasn't enough.</i>

37:24.500 --> 37:28.625
<i>What do you think? Should we leave</i>
<i>it there tonight? It's getting late.</i>

37:30.875 --> 37:32.875
<i>I mean, I can come back next year.</i>

37:34.625 --> 37:36.541
<i>I'm just kidding. I'll crack on.</i>

37:36.625 --> 37:37.791
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

37:39.583 --> 37:42.708
<i>Nikolas was lying there in the snow,</i>

37:43.875 --> 37:46.166
<i>frozen and forgotten.</i>

37:47.375 --> 37:49.750
<i>Nikolas. Wake up, please.</i>

37:50.833 --> 37:51.833
<i>[gasps]</i>

37:53.833 --> 37:55.041
<i>Nikolas, hey.</i>

37:55.125 --> 37:58.000
<i>[Aunt Ruth]</i> When suddenly,
there was a noise.

37:58.083 --> 38:00.541
<i>-[bells tinkling]</i>
<i>-You hear that? Somebody's…</i>

38:01.333 --> 38:02.583
<i>Somebody's coming closer.</i>

38:03.500 --> 38:07.375
<i>Oh, they're here to help.</i>
<i>Nikolas, we're safe. We're--</i>

38:07.458 --> 38:08.750
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

38:13.500 --> 38:14.333
<i>No, we're doomed.</i>

38:17.958 --> 38:18.791
<i>[gasps]</i>

38:20.291 --> 38:21.375
<i>[quavering]</i>

38:30.708 --> 38:33.125
<i>Look at his strange ears, Grandpapa.</i>

38:33.208 --> 38:35.375
<i>Human ears can take a lot</i>
<i>of getting used to.</i>

38:37.500 --> 38:40.125
<i>He's a human. Will he eat us?</i>

38:40.208 --> 38:42.083
<i>Oh no, no. We're quite safe.</i>

38:43.500 --> 38:47.375
<i>-But what about what happened--</i>
<i>-We must always help those in trouble.</i>

38:47.958 --> 38:49.625
<i>Even if they are human.</i>

39:04.750 --> 39:06.750
<i>[twinkling]</i>

39:10.958 --> 39:13.541
<i>-[crackling]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas gasps]</i>

39:14.833 --> 39:17.000
<i>Where am I? Who are you?</i>

39:17.083 --> 39:18.083
<i>I'm Little Noosh.</i>

39:18.166 --> 39:20.041
<i>And I am Father Topo.</i>

39:20.125 --> 39:24.750
<i>Noosh's great-great-grandfather,</i>
<i>if you can believe that.</i>

39:26.833 --> 39:27.875
<i>Am I dead?</i>

39:27.958 --> 39:31.541
<i>No, Grandpapa just worked</i>
<i>a little drimwick on you.</i>

39:32.333 --> 39:34.333
<i>-What's a drimwick?</i>
<i>-Yeah, what's a drimwick?</i>

39:34.416 --> 39:36.583
<i>A drimwick is a hope spell.</i>

39:37.250 --> 39:41.625
<i>I hoped for you to be strong</i>
<i>and warm and always safe.</i>

39:42.125 --> 39:44.833
<i>-Always safe? That's impossible.</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

39:44.916 --> 39:48.333
<i>We… We never ever say that word.</i>

39:48.416 --> 39:54.625
<i>Uh, an impossibility is only a possibility</i>
<i>that you don't understand yet.</i>

39:54.708 --> 39:57.750
<i>But now we must get as far away</i>
<i>from you as possible.</i>

39:57.833 --> 39:59.500
<i>And you must leave Elfhelm.</i>

40:00.083 --> 40:03.250
<i>Elfhelm? The elf village?</i>
<i>But I'm not even there.</i>

40:03.333 --> 40:05.166
<i>[giggles] You silly.</i>

40:05.250 --> 40:07.958
<i>We're standing at the bottom</i>
<i>of the street of Seven Curves,</i>

40:08.041 --> 40:09.833
<i>the longest street in Elfhelm.</i>

40:09.916 --> 40:12.583
<i>I'm sorry. We're in the middle of nowhere.</i>

40:13.458 --> 40:14.541
<i>There's just snow.</i>

40:15.583 --> 40:16.666
<i>Is he blind?</i>

40:17.333 --> 40:18.958
<i>He doesn't know how to see.</i>

40:19.041 --> 40:22.083
<i>[Nikolas] Wait, I've risked everything</i>
<i>to find Elfhelm.</i>

40:23.708 --> 40:27.083
<i>You have to let me see it. Just once.</i>

40:29.666 --> 40:30.875
<i>To see something…</i>

40:33.166 --> 40:34.666
<i>you must believe in it.</i>

40:35.625 --> 40:37.625
<i>Really believe.</i>

40:39.791 --> 40:40.750
<i>Go ahead.</i>

40:41.375 --> 40:42.750
<i>Try your hardest,</i>

40:43.291 --> 40:46.125
<i>and see if you can see what</i>
<i>it is you're searching for.</i>

40:46.208 --> 40:48.208
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

41:03.375 --> 41:04.416
<i>[Father Topo] Go on.</i>

41:05.666 --> 41:06.833
<i>Believe!</i>

41:21.166 --> 41:23.166
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

41:25.541 --> 41:26.625
<i>Elfhelm.</i>

41:34.208 --> 41:36.208
<i>[music intensifies]</i>

41:39.250 --> 41:40.500
<i>[elves laughing]</i>

41:47.375 --> 41:49.166
<i>[indistinct yelling]</i>

41:57.166 --> 41:59.166
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

42:03.083 --> 42:06.375
<i>[Miika] Wait a licking minute.</i>
<i>What is this?</i>

42:07.291 --> 42:08.750
<i>-[Nikolas] Elfhelm.</i>
<i>-[Miika chuckles]</i>

42:08.833 --> 42:10.958
<i>-[Miika] Look at it!</i>
<i>-It's incredible!</i>

42:11.041 --> 42:12.125
<i>[Miika laughs]</i>

42:12.833 --> 42:16.750
<i>Oh! I'm gonna be honest, kid.</i>
<i>I did not see this one working out for us.</i>

42:16.833 --> 42:19.625
<i>Yes, and now you've seen our home,</i>

42:19.708 --> 42:23.000
<i>please take your reindeer</i>
<i>and your mouse and… and go.</i>

42:23.083 --> 42:25.541
<i>Whatever it is you're looking for,</i>
<i>you won't find it here.</i>

42:25.625 --> 42:29.583
<i>I came to find my father. I traveled</i>
<i>a long way to give him this hat.</i>

42:29.666 --> 42:32.500
<i>-[elf] Get out of the way! Move it.</i>
<i>-Quick. Shh!</i>

42:33.083 --> 42:34.458
<i>We're already too late.</i>

42:36.250 --> 42:38.166
<i>-In here.</i>
<i>-[guard] Get back to work!</i>

42:38.250 --> 42:39.291
<i>-[clangs]</i>
<i>-Ooh.</i>

42:40.541 --> 42:41.541
<i>[grunts]</i>

42:45.875 --> 42:46.958
<i>Why are we hiding?</i>

42:47.708 --> 42:48.708
<i>Not now.</i>

42:51.500 --> 42:53.416
<i>-[Nikolas] Who's Little Kip?</i>
<i>-[Father Topo] What?</i>

42:53.500 --> 42:54.708
<i>Who is Little Kip?</i>

42:56.708 --> 42:58.166
<i>[little elf] Hey, you dippy!</i>

42:58.250 --> 42:59.375
<i>We have to go.</i>

42:59.458 --> 43:00.333
<i>[guard] Stop her!</i>

43:00.416 --> 43:02.875
<i>-This way.</i>
<i>-[guard] Wipe that smile off your face!</i>

43:03.791 --> 43:04.791
<i>Up there.</i>

43:05.541 --> 43:09.208
<i>-[goat bleating]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] I don't understand any of this.</i>

43:09.291 --> 43:13.000
<i>I thought Elfhelm was the happiest,</i>
<i>most magical place in the world.</i>

43:13.083 --> 43:14.750
<i>-It was.</i>
<i>-And will be again.</i>

43:14.833 --> 43:17.000
<i>That's what we in the Resistance believe.</i>

43:17.083 --> 43:18.500
<i>-[whistles]</i>
<i>-The Resistance?</i>

43:19.666 --> 43:20.666
<i>[whistles]</i>

43:21.708 --> 43:23.416
<i>What do you mean, Resistance?</i>

43:23.500 --> 43:24.708
<i>[Father Topo] Quick! In.</i>

43:25.833 --> 43:26.666
<i>In!</i>

43:28.166 --> 43:29.625
<i>-[whistles]</i>
<i>-[elf whistles]</i>

43:31.583 --> 43:32.791
<i>[door clangs close]</i>

43:36.500 --> 43:38.250
<i>[Father Topo] Listen, human…</i>

43:38.333 --> 43:40.541
<i>[soft thumping]</i>

43:40.625 --> 43:43.458
<i>…when you go in there, just, um…</i>

43:45.250 --> 43:46.250
<i>Well, you'll see.</i>

43:47.500 --> 43:48.375
<i>Go where?</i>

43:50.333 --> 43:52.333
<i>[thumping gets louder]</i>

43:56.166 --> 43:58.416
<i>-[bell ringing in rhythm]</i>
<i>-Give me your hand.</i>

43:59.000 --> 44:00.291
<i>[elf 1] Merry Christmas!</i>

44:00.375 --> 44:02.250
<i>-[folk music playing]</i>
<i>-[laughter]</i>

44:03.333 --> 44:04.750
<i>[elf 2] Give us another twirl!</i>

44:05.708 --> 44:06.708
<i>[elf 1] Merry Christmas!</i>

44:06.791 --> 44:08.041
<i>[elf 2] Merry Christmas!</i>

44:08.125 --> 44:09.666
<i>[Father Topo] Well, there you have it.</i>

44:09.750 --> 44:11.750
<i>[music continues]</i>

44:15.250 --> 44:17.458
<i>-[elf 3] Merry!</i>
<i>-[goat bleating]</i>

44:17.541 --> 44:20.500
<i>This is the Resistance.</i>

44:20.583 --> 44:21.833
<i>To what? Sanity?</i>

44:21.916 --> 44:23.458
<i>[elf 2] Merry, Merry, Christmas!</i>

44:23.541 --> 44:24.833
<i>[elf 1] Merry Christmas!</i>

44:25.666 --> 44:28.833
<i>Nikolas! Nikolas, what is this?</i>

44:28.916 --> 44:31.083
<i>[chuckling]</i>

44:31.166 --> 44:32.916
<i>It's… It's cake city!</i>

44:34.375 --> 44:35.875
<i>[sniffing]</i>

44:35.958 --> 44:37.083
<i>That's incredible.</i>

44:37.875 --> 44:39.333
<i>Hey there, beautiful. [licks]</i>

44:40.166 --> 44:42.000
<i>Wait there. I'll be right back.</i>

44:42.083 --> 44:43.583
<i>[music continues]</i>

44:47.125 --> 44:50.166
<i>No idea what</i>
<i>this Christmas thing is, but I love it.</i>

44:50.916 --> 44:52.500
<i>[munching]</i>

44:53.375 --> 44:56.458
<i>Hey, Nikolas,</i>
<i>guess who just ate a chair. [yelps]</i>

44:57.000 --> 45:00.708
<i>Oh, don't worry, sugar glass.</i>
<i>I'm fine and stuffed.</i>

45:01.291 --> 45:02.875
<i>[Little Noosh] Help yourself. It's yummy.</i>

45:02.958 --> 45:05.958
<i>-[Miika] I couldn't eat another thing.</i>
<i>-[elf 1] Merry Christmas!</i>

45:06.041 --> 45:08.208
<i>-So good.</i>
<i>-Give me a bite.</i>

45:08.291 --> 45:11.208
<i>-[Nikolas] Father Topo.</i>
<i>-Yeah. Hmm?</i>

45:11.291 --> 45:13.458
<i>Did they just say Christmas?</i>

45:13.541 --> 45:15.375
<i>Yes, this is a Christmas party.</i>

45:16.083 --> 45:19.916
<i>What is Christmas?</i>
<i>That's the name my mother used to call me.</i>

45:20.000 --> 45:21.125
<i>I beg your pardon.</i>

45:21.875 --> 45:24.500
<i>Did you just say what is Christmas?</i>

45:25.500 --> 45:27.333
<i>-Yes?</i>
<i>-Apologies for my friend.</i>

45:27.416 --> 45:31.250
<i>He's a simpleton. A Christmas</i>
<i>is a city made of cakes, isn't it?</i>

45:31.333 --> 45:35.041
<i>That's the saddest thing</i>
<i>I've ever heard in my entire life.</i>

45:35.125 --> 45:38.666
<i>Christmas is the greatest day of all</i>
<i>because it is the kindest day of all.</i>

45:38.750 --> 45:40.291
<i>And the brightest and the smiley-est.</i>

45:40.375 --> 45:43.250
<i>A day when being openhearted</i>
<i>is the most important thing of all,</i>

45:43.333 --> 45:45.750
<i>which is why</i>
<i>we won't let them take it from us.</i>

45:45.833 --> 45:47.916
<i>[sputtering] Enough, Little Noosh.</i>

45:48.000 --> 45:50.125
<i>It is time to talk of easier things.</i>

45:50.208 --> 45:54.125
<i>Now we have told you our names,</i>
<i>but you have yet to tell us yours.</i>

45:54.208 --> 45:56.000
<i>-Name's Miika. Okay.</i>
<i>-I'm Nikolas.</i>

45:56.083 --> 46:00.166
<i>[laughs] Oh, that cheered me right up.</i>
<i>That sounds like Nekilas.</i>

46:00.250 --> 46:03.791
<i>My word. Yes, it does.</i>
<i>Nekilas. Nekilas. [chuckles]</i>

46:03.875 --> 46:05.541
<i>Nekilas. Bleh.</i>

46:05.625 --> 46:07.708
<i>-Nekilas is bad because…</i>
<i>-[knocking on door]</i>

46:07.791 --> 46:11.000
<i>It's a rather smelly sausage</i>
<i>only eaten by trolls.</i>

46:11.083 --> 46:13.000
<i>-[door opens]</i>
<i>-Trolls exist too?</i>

46:13.083 --> 46:15.750
<i>-[screaming] Raid!</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

46:15.833 --> 46:17.625
<i>-Run! Run!</i>
<i>-[all screaming]</i>

46:18.208 --> 46:20.291
<i>[elf] Run! Run!</i>

46:20.375 --> 46:22.250
<i>Everybody, get down!</i>

46:22.333 --> 46:26.250
<i>-You heard the elf. Get down.</i>
<i>-Don't you point that thing at me.</i>

46:27.333 --> 46:28.333
<i>Sorry, Mum.</i>

46:28.416 --> 46:30.500
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

46:49.375 --> 46:51.750
<i>-What's going on?</i>
<i>-Shh! Shh!</i>

46:52.625 --> 46:53.875
<i>-[loud thud]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

46:53.958 --> 46:55.083
<i>[door creaking]</i>

47:05.458 --> 47:07.208
<i>-[clatters]</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

47:08.958 --> 47:10.875
<i>-[clatters]</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

47:13.750 --> 47:15.458
<i>[elves quavering]</i>

47:19.125 --> 47:20.375
<i>[staff thuds]</i>

47:24.208 --> 47:25.750
<i>So the rumors are true.</i>

47:28.583 --> 47:31.333
<i>There are still elves that like to party.</i>

47:31.416 --> 47:33.291
<i>-Mother Vodal--</i>
<i>-Quiet!</i>

47:39.375 --> 47:41.333
<i>Have we learnt nothing?</i>

47:43.791 --> 47:47.958
<i>Has the suffering of the past months</i>
<i>made us not a jot wiser?</i>

47:50.708 --> 47:53.833
<i>Are the new rules to be completely igno--</i>

47:54.750 --> 47:56.000
<i>[Miika sniffing]</i>

47:57.791 --> 48:02.625
<i>Who or rather what is that?</i>

48:04.416 --> 48:05.875
<i>-I'm--</i>
<i>-My name's Miika, Mum.</i>

48:05.958 --> 48:09.500
<i>-Have you never seen a mouse before?</i>
<i>-I have. I wasn't addressing you.</i>

48:09.583 --> 48:10.875
<i>My most humble apologies.</i>

48:10.958 --> 48:13.041
<i>-I'm Nikolas.</i>
<i>-But it wasn't clear.</i>

48:13.666 --> 48:15.625
<i>-I'm human.</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

48:15.708 --> 48:16.958
<i>[elves murmuring]</i>

48:17.541 --> 48:21.125
<i>I see that too. I just don't believe it.</i>

48:24.833 --> 48:30.583
<i>Father Topo, unless I'm much mistaken,</i>
<i>which I never am,</i>

48:30.666 --> 48:34.708
<i>you were at the last council meeting.</i>

48:34.791 --> 48:36.083
<i>Yes. I was.</i>

48:37.333 --> 48:41.125
<i>It was at that meeting that the new rules</i>
<i>for elves were introduced.</i>

48:41.208 --> 48:44.416
<i>The most important</i>
<i>and least breakable being</i>

48:45.125 --> 48:50.583
<i>that no humans</i>
<i>can ever, ever be brought here.</i>

48:50.666 --> 48:53.458
<i>But I… I didn't bring him here.</i>

48:53.541 --> 48:55.333
<i>[elves murmuring]</i>

48:55.416 --> 48:56.416
<i>I found him.</i>

48:57.458 --> 48:59.291
<i>-A whisker from death.</i>
<i>-Oh.</i>

48:59.875 --> 49:05.083
<i>So I… I performed a… a small hope spell.</i>

49:05.166 --> 49:06.541
<i>A drimwick.</i>

49:07.625 --> 49:08.541
<i>[scoffs nervously]</i>

49:09.500 --> 49:10.541
<i>On a human.</i>

49:12.041 --> 49:13.041
<i>Little one.</i>

49:16.041 --> 49:18.208
<i>-[whooshes]</i>
<i>-[angrily] You fool.</i>

49:19.416 --> 49:21.666
<i>Who knows what power you've unleashed!</i>

49:21.750 --> 49:24.458
<i>Please, it was the only way</i>
<i>I could save him.</i>

49:24.541 --> 49:28.708
<i>Let us remember</i>
<i>the way things were before.</i>

49:28.791 --> 49:30.875
<i>We are elves.</i>

49:30.958 --> 49:33.166
<i>We… we use our powers for good.</i>

49:33.250 --> 49:36.375
<i>What good is that</i>
<i>when we are under attack?</i>

49:37.500 --> 49:39.166
<i>We must adapt.</i>

49:41.000 --> 49:42.875
<i>We must send a clear message</i>

49:42.958 --> 49:45.750
<i>that no outsiders</i>
<i>are allowed here anymore.</i>

49:46.625 --> 49:50.750
<i>It was on this platform</i>
<i>that I was elected holder of the staff.</i>

49:51.500 --> 49:53.083
<i>Ruler of Elfhelm.</i>

49:53.166 --> 49:55.250
<i>But in fairness, Mother Vodal--</i>

49:55.333 --> 49:57.375
<i>-Be quiet!</i>
<i>-[Father Topo yelps]</i>

49:57.458 --> 49:58.458
<i>[elves scream]</i>

49:59.083 --> 50:00.083
<i>[thuds]</i>

50:01.208 --> 50:02.041
<i>Uh…</i>

50:04.250 --> 50:05.875
<i>[whooshes]</i>

50:08.208 --> 50:13.208
<i>Now, human, tell me why you came here.</i>

50:13.291 --> 50:15.708
<i>-I came to look for my father.</i>
<i>-Your father?</i>

50:15.791 --> 50:19.208
<i>Yes. He came to Elfhelm</i>
<i>to try and find something magical.</i>

50:19.291 --> 50:20.458
<i>She doesn't need to know that.</i>

50:20.541 --> 50:24.125
<i>Did he travel, by chance,</i>
<i>with a group of other men?</i>

50:24.208 --> 50:27.833
<i>Yes. Have you seen him?</i>
<i>Did he actually make it to Elfhelm?</i>

50:27.916 --> 50:31.208
<i>Oh, he was here all right.</i>
<i>He was one of them.</i>

50:31.833 --> 50:33.833
<i>[chairs creaking]</i>

50:34.375 --> 50:35.833
<i>-[staff thuds]</i>
<i>-[chairs crash]</i>

50:35.916 --> 50:37.458
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>
<i>-[whooshing]</i>

50:41.375 --> 50:42.541
<i>What did you do to him?</i>

50:43.416 --> 50:45.000
<i>I trusted him.</i>

50:46.166 --> 50:47.375
<i>We all did.</i>

50:48.625 --> 50:49.583
<i>And why not?</i>

50:51.166 --> 50:54.083
<i>A human had visited us once before…</i>

50:56.375 --> 50:57.541
<i>too briefly.</i>

50:59.125 --> 51:01.291
<i>And her stay brought us such joy.</i>

51:03.791 --> 51:08.333
<i>For years we waited ready to welcome</i>
<i>any others who found their way to Elfhelm</i>

51:09.333 --> 51:11.041
<i>to show them good will,</i>

51:12.541 --> 51:16.250
<i>which these men proved</i>
<i>was just another name for weakness.</i>

51:16.333 --> 51:17.375
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

51:17.458 --> 51:20.291
<i>I'm speaking,</i>
<i>of course, of poor Little Kip.</i>

51:20.375 --> 51:21.458
<i>Who's Little Kip?</i>

51:24.166 --> 51:26.708
<i>Little Kip's parents are here.</i>
<i>You can ask them yourself.</i>

51:28.166 --> 51:30.458
<i>Please tell me. What did these men do?</i>

51:33.583 --> 51:35.166
<i>Speak! Answer him!</i>

51:35.833 --> 51:38.625
<i>-They took our boy.</i>
<i>-They kidnapped Little Kip.</i>

51:38.708 --> 51:42.500
<i>No! You must be wrong.</i>
<i>My father would never do such a thing.</i>

51:42.583 --> 51:43.625
<i>And yet he did.</i>

51:44.708 --> 51:47.666
<i>Which is why at the election,</i>
<i>I put myself forward</i>

51:48.166 --> 51:50.458
<i>with the motto, "Elves for Elves."</i>

51:51.041 --> 51:54.041
<i>No more silly parties</i>
<i>where we let our guards down.</i>

51:54.125 --> 51:56.291
<i>No more wanton carelessness.</i>

51:57.708 --> 51:59.000
<i>No more singing.</i>

51:59.500 --> 52:03.416
<i>And an outright ban on spickle dancing!</i>

52:03.500 --> 52:04.625
<i>[elves gasp]</i>

52:05.541 --> 52:06.375
<i>[thudding]</i>

52:06.458 --> 52:07.625
<i>No more kindness.</i>

52:08.291 --> 52:09.166
<i>[thudding]</i>

52:09.250 --> 52:10.541
<i>No more joy.</i>

52:11.625 --> 52:12.458
<i>[staff thuds]</i>

52:13.083 --> 52:15.333
<i>No more Christmas.</i>

52:15.416 --> 52:18.583
<i>Guards! Take him to the tower!</i>

52:19.875 --> 52:20.750
<i>[guard] Move it.</i>

52:23.375 --> 52:24.375
<i>Give me that.</i>

52:24.875 --> 52:26.375
<i>[gasps]</i>

52:29.750 --> 52:30.916
<i>-Miika.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

52:31.708 --> 52:35.041
<i>-Get out of here while you still can.</i>
<i>-No, I'm not gonna leave you.</i>

52:35.125 --> 52:37.208
<i>We don't know what's waiting</i>
<i>for us in that dark tower.</i>

52:37.291 --> 52:39.916
<i>[Miika] I'm not gonna--</i>
<i>Wait, what could be up there?</i>

52:40.000 --> 52:42.916
<i>It could be torture,</i>
<i>dismemberment, or even death.</i>

52:43.000 --> 52:44.000
<i>[guard] What's that? Hey!</i>

52:44.083 --> 52:45.250
<i>-Nikolas!</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] Miika!</i>

52:45.333 --> 52:46.708
<i>[guard] He's smuggling a mouse!</i>

52:47.208 --> 52:49.250
<i>Move it! You're on your own now.</i>

52:51.125 --> 52:52.166
<i>[shuddering]</i>

52:52.250 --> 52:53.750
<i>[breathes deeply]</i>

52:54.666 --> 52:55.625
<i>[shuddering]</i>

52:55.708 --> 52:57.708
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

53:03.750 --> 53:05.666
<i>-[guard] Get through that door.</i>
<i>-[Nikolas grunts]</i>

53:05.750 --> 53:07.750
<i>[ticking]</i>

53:11.500 --> 53:12.958
<i>[mechanical whirring]</i>

53:15.375 --> 53:16.791
<i>[Nikolas] Where are you taking me?</i>

53:17.583 --> 53:18.416
<i>[guard] Get in!</i>

53:21.333 --> 53:24.541
<i>Please, if I could just find my father,</i>
<i>I'm sure he'd clear it all up.</i>

53:25.125 --> 53:28.333
<i>-Please, I'm telling the truth!</i>
<i>-[female voice laughing]</i>

53:29.333 --> 53:31.541
<i>-[fluttering]</i>
<i>-Please, I'm telling the truth. [laughs]</i>

53:34.750 --> 53:37.166
<i>You don't know</i>
<i>the first thing about truth.</i>

53:41.125 --> 53:42.125
<i>Nobody does.</i>

53:43.833 --> 53:45.875
<i>My lonely heart is the proof.</i>

53:46.583 --> 53:48.500
<i>Um, are you an elf?</i>

53:48.583 --> 53:50.833
<i>No, gross. I'm a pixie.</i>

53:52.375 --> 53:53.250
<i>Truth Pixie.</i>

53:54.875 --> 53:57.166
<i>You must be lying. There's no such thing.</i>

53:57.250 --> 54:01.375
<i>I can't lie. I'm a truth pixie.</i>
<i>That gets me into trouble.</i>

54:02.041 --> 54:04.041
<i>That and making people's heads explode,</i>
<i>but I mean--</i>

54:04.125 --> 54:05.250
<i>[fluttering]</i>

54:06.041 --> 54:07.166
<i>Wait, what?</i>

54:07.250 --> 54:08.708
<i>[fluttering]</i>

54:08.791 --> 54:10.625
<i>[laughs]</i>

54:10.708 --> 54:13.791
<i>Okay, so what I do is I slip a hewlip leaf</i>
<i>into someone's mouth,</i>

54:13.875 --> 54:17.333
<i>and 12 seconds later,</i>
<i>they explode. [laughing]</i>

54:19.583 --> 54:23.500
<i>Look, I need to find my father.</i>
<i>Could you help me?</i>

54:23.583 --> 54:27.166
<i>I could, but I don't want to.</i>

54:27.708 --> 54:28.541
<i>[laughs]</i>

54:28.625 --> 54:32.833
<i>I told you I never lie,</i>
<i>and saving your father doesn't sound fun.</i>

54:34.666 --> 54:37.250
<i>How about Little Kip?</i>
<i>What do you know about him?</i>

54:38.250 --> 54:39.750
<i>He's got a funny name.</i>

54:39.833 --> 54:42.666
<i>-Humans kidnapped him--</i>
<i>-No, it's all a big misunderstanding.</i>

54:42.750 --> 54:45.000
<i>If I could find my father,</i>
<i>I'm sure he'd clear it all up.</i>

54:45.083 --> 54:48.208
<i>Argh! What a boring idea.</i>
<i>Good thing we're locked up in here.</i>

54:48.791 --> 54:51.083
<i>-Oh yes, hold this.</i>
<i>-What?</i>

54:52.208 --> 54:55.458
<i>-Ouch!</i>
<i>-[laughing] I'm calling them crackers.</i>

54:55.541 --> 54:58.916
<i>Not quite as potent as hewlip,</i>
<i>but plenty of trouble in the right hands.</i>

54:59.000 --> 55:01.083
<i>-What was that for?</i>
<i>-Waking up the troll.</i>

55:01.166 --> 55:04.375
<i>-What troll?</i>
<i>-The one right behind you.</i>

55:04.458 --> 55:05.541
<i>[troll grunts]</i>

55:07.791 --> 55:10.541
<i>[yawning]</i>

55:11.750 --> 55:13.500
<i>-[Truth Pixie giggling]</i>
<i>-[sniffing]</i>

55:15.750 --> 55:17.250
<i>-Huh?</i>
<i>-[Nikolas gasps]</i>

55:17.875 --> 55:19.541
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

55:19.625 --> 55:21.208
<i>-[roaring]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

55:21.291 --> 55:22.916
<i>[screaming]</i>

55:25.458 --> 55:28.000
<i>I would recommend</i>
<i>you squeeze the head until it pops,</i>

55:28.083 --> 55:31.333
<i>suck out all the juicy bits</i>
<i>and then work your way down to the toes.</i>

55:31.416 --> 55:33.500
<i>[screams] Are you insane?</i>

55:33.583 --> 55:35.375
<i>I'm sorry. It just comes out.</i>

55:35.458 --> 55:38.041
<i>-[growls]</i>
<i>-Ahh! Can you help me, please?</i>

55:38.125 --> 55:39.291
<i>[groans]</i>

55:39.375 --> 55:42.416
<i>[Nikolas] I thought</i>
<i>you have to tell the truth. [grunts]</i>

55:42.500 --> 55:46.166
<i>I do have one hewlip leaf left,</i>
<i>but I'm saving up something special.</i>

55:46.250 --> 55:48.375
<i>[Nikolas] This is special.</i>
<i>I'm being eaten!</i>

55:48.458 --> 55:49.583
<i>[troll grunting]</i>

55:49.666 --> 55:51.791
<i>-Okay, fine.</i>
<i>-[troll grunting]</i>

55:53.416 --> 55:54.458
<i>[Truth Pixie grunts]</i>

55:56.666 --> 55:57.875
<i>[Nikolas grunts]</i>

55:57.958 --> 55:59.000
<i>[Truth Pixie grunts]</i>

56:00.500 --> 56:01.958
<i>-Grab it!</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

56:02.833 --> 56:04.916
<i>-Shove it in his mouth!</i>
<i>-Aah!</i>

56:07.458 --> 56:08.625
<i>[gags]</i>

56:09.666 --> 56:11.416
<i>-[laughs]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

56:13.750 --> 56:14.833
<i>[gasps]</i>

56:14.916 --> 56:20.375
<i>Nine, eight, seven, six…</i>

56:20.875 --> 56:21.708
<i>Hold my hand.</i>

56:21.791 --> 56:23.416
<i>-[giggling]</i>
<i>-[whooshes]</i>

56:23.916 --> 56:25.625
<i>[Truth Pixie] Three, two…</i>

56:26.666 --> 56:28.458
<i>-[explosion]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas screams]</i>

56:28.541 --> 56:30.541
<i>[both screaming]</i>

56:31.208 --> 56:32.041
<i>We're flying!</i>

56:32.125 --> 56:34.666
<i>More like not dropping.</i>
<i>Have you been exposed to magic recently?</i>

56:34.750 --> 56:36.708
<i>I was drimwicked,</i>
<i>but I'm not sure what that means.</i>

56:36.791 --> 56:38.791
<i>A drimwick is a boring type of elf magic.</i>

56:38.875 --> 56:40.833
<i>It only works</i>
<i>if you're thinking of something good.</i>

56:40.916 --> 56:44.583
<i>I was thinking about people and things</i>
<i>I love, my mother, my father, and Miika.</i>

56:44.666 --> 56:46.500
<i>-Who's Miika?</i>
<i>-He's my mouse friend.</i>

56:46.583 --> 56:49.625
<i>How fun! I've never</i>
<i>blown up a mouse before. [chuckles]</i>

56:50.208 --> 56:51.958
<i>[screams] Now what's happening?</i>

56:52.041 --> 56:53.875
<i>[Truth Pixie] I think</i>
<i>I spoiled the moment.</i>

56:53.958 --> 56:55.541
<i>[Nikolas] I'm picturing beautiful things.</i>

56:55.625 --> 56:57.333
<i>[Truth Pixie] I'm thinking</i>
<i>of a dead mouse.</i>

56:57.416 --> 56:59.541
<i>[Nikolas] Now that's all</i>
<i>I can picture too!</i>

57:00.458 --> 57:02.000
<i>[screams]</i>

57:02.083 --> 57:03.791
<i>[Truth Pixie grunting]</i>

57:04.916 --> 57:07.333
<i>[guard 1] Where are they? Where are they?</i>

57:07.416 --> 57:09.666
<i>-[guard 2] Come along quickly!</i>
<i>-[guard 3] Move!</i>

57:09.750 --> 57:11.333
<i>-Hurry up.</i>
<i>-Out of the way.</i>

57:11.416 --> 57:13.000
<i>[guard 1] Anyone seen them?</i>

57:13.083 --> 57:14.333
<i>-Come on.</i>
<i>-Why?</i>

57:14.416 --> 57:17.666
<i>-[guard 1] Where are they?</i>
<i>-Oh, yoo-hoo! Hi! We're up here!</i>

57:17.750 --> 57:20.750
<i>-[Nikolas] What are you doing?</i>
<i>-On the roof. There they are.</i>

57:20.833 --> 57:21.791
<i>[muffled yell]</i>

57:21.875 --> 57:25.375
<i>-No! How about just not saying anything?</i>
<i>-I wish I could.</i>

57:25.458 --> 57:26.375
<i>[Nikolas panting]</i>

57:26.458 --> 57:28.083
<i>You know how many people want</i>
<i>to be friends</i>

57:28.166 --> 57:30.125
<i>with someone who only speaks the truth?</i>

57:30.666 --> 57:33.791
<i>-Not many?</i>
<i>-Not any, human boy.</i>

57:35.041 --> 57:38.625
<i>Listen, I really can't keep</i>
<i>calling you human boy,</i>

57:38.708 --> 57:41.541
<i>even though you're</i>
<i>a particularly perfect example of one.</i>

57:42.083 --> 57:46.500
<i>Let's be honest, I'm not in a position</i>
<i>to be turning away friend material.</i>

57:46.583 --> 57:49.208
<i>So, new friend, what should I call you?</i>

57:49.291 --> 57:51.166
<i>My mom used to call me Christmas,</i>

57:52.333 --> 57:54.083
<i>but everyone else calls me Nikolas.</i>

57:54.750 --> 57:58.041
<i>In conclusion,</i>
<i>humans are dangerous animals</i>

57:58.125 --> 57:59.625
<i>and can never be trusted.</i>

57:59.708 --> 58:00.541
<i>[door opens]</i>

58:00.625 --> 58:04.041
<i>So, what would we do</i>
<i>if we ever saw a human?</i>

58:04.125 --> 58:05.250
<i>[girl screams]</i>

58:05.333 --> 58:06.708
<i>That's absolutely right.</i>

58:06.791 --> 58:08.875
<i>[all screaming]</i>

58:11.250 --> 58:13.500
<i>Please, you have to help me escape.</i>

58:13.583 --> 58:15.333
<i>Strictly speaking, you don't.</i>

58:15.916 --> 58:19.916
<i>I am duty-bound to protect my students</i>
<i>from those who would do them harm,</i>

58:20.000 --> 58:21.791
<i>like the humans who kidnapped Little Kip.</i>

58:22.875 --> 58:23.958
<i>-[bell tolls]</i>
<i>-No, please.</i>

58:24.625 --> 58:26.000
<i>If you help me escape,</i>

58:26.625 --> 58:29.375
<i>I'll find Little Kip</i>
<i>and I'll bring him back to Elfhelm.</i>

58:29.458 --> 58:31.625
<i>-[knocking on door]</i>
<i>-[guard] Open this door.</i>

58:31.708 --> 58:33.291
<i>Please. I'm telling the truth.</i>

58:33.875 --> 58:35.125
<i>[banging on door]</i>

58:35.208 --> 58:38.166
<i>[guard] Open up! That's an order!</i>

58:39.750 --> 58:40.791
<i>-Stand back!</i>
<i>-Why?</i>

58:41.291 --> 58:43.041
<i>[grunts] Hurry!</i>

58:43.125 --> 58:44.208
<i>[gasps, squeals]</i>

58:44.291 --> 58:46.000
<i>[giggles]</i>

58:46.083 --> 58:47.916
<i>[teacher] Go! Bring back Little Kip!</i>

58:48.416 --> 58:50.500
<i>[adventurous music playing]</i>

58:51.416 --> 58:52.875
<i>[Truth pixie chuckling]</i>

58:54.625 --> 58:55.625
<i>[guard yelling]</i>

58:55.708 --> 58:56.583
<i>That's it!</i>

58:57.625 --> 58:58.958
<i>Any humans in here?</i>

59:00.958 --> 59:03.000
<i>Um, can I be excused?</i>

59:07.000 --> 59:09.166
<i>-What about you? You a human?</i>
<i>-No.</i>

59:11.000 --> 59:11.833
<i>We're good here.</i>

59:11.916 --> 59:13.458
<i>-[yells]</i>
<i>-[thuds on ground]</i>

59:16.125 --> 59:17.875
<i>[guard] Look in all the houses!</i>

59:19.083 --> 59:20.708
<i>[guards yelling indistinctly]</i>

59:21.583 --> 59:22.416
<i>This way.</i>

59:23.541 --> 59:25.166
<i>-[guard 1] This way.</i>
<i>-[guard 2 yelling]</i>

59:25.250 --> 59:26.291
<i>-Nikolas!</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

59:26.375 --> 59:28.291
<i>It's okay. I know this reindeer.</i>

59:28.958 --> 59:30.708
<i>-[bellows]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] Thanks, Noosh.</i>

59:30.791 --> 59:32.500
<i>Hello, boy. I missed you too.</i>

59:33.041 --> 59:35.041
<i>-[guard 3] There they are!</i>
<i>-Oh no.</i>

59:35.125 --> 59:36.375
<i>-We got them!</i>
<i>-Time to move.</i>

59:36.458 --> 59:37.833
<i>-Don't let them get away!</i>
<i>-Hurry up!</i>

59:37.916 --> 59:39.916
<i>-[Nikolas] Grab hold!</i>
<i>-Come on, let's go!</i>

59:40.875 --> 59:43.500
<i>-Go on, Blitzen.</i>
<i>-Move it, kid!</i>

59:44.125 --> 59:45.666
<i>Good luck, smelly sausage!</i>

59:45.750 --> 59:47.500
<i>[Miika] Nikolas! Up here!</i>

59:48.458 --> 59:49.291
<i>Miika!</i>

59:50.333 --> 59:51.625
<i>[screaming]</i>

59:52.250 --> 59:55.000
<i>-[Nikolas] Miika, I missed you.</i>
<i>-I missed you with all my heart.</i>

59:55.083 --> 59:56.958
<i>-Miika, meet Truth Pixie.</i>
<i>-Sorry, who is this?</i>

59:57.041 --> 1:00:00.125
<i>[Mother Vodal] No! Do not let him escape!</i>

1:00:00.208 --> 1:00:01.541
<i>[yelling]</i>

1:00:02.041 --> 1:00:03.208
<i>[guard yells]</i>

1:00:03.291 --> 1:00:05.500
<i>-[panting]</i>
<i>-Bit big for a pixie.</i>

1:00:05.583 --> 1:00:07.375
<i>-Excuse me?</i>
<i>-Guys, not now.</i>

1:00:07.458 --> 1:00:08.875
<i>Who's this knob? Another new friend?</i>

1:00:08.958 --> 1:00:10.541
<i>-[grunting]</i>
<i>-[yelps]</i>

1:00:10.625 --> 1:00:12.416
<i>[guards yelling]</i>

1:00:12.500 --> 1:00:13.500
<i>-[whooshes]</i>
<i>-[yells]</i>

1:00:16.083 --> 1:00:17.000
<i>[guard] Stop him!</i>

1:00:17.666 --> 1:00:19.083
<i>[Nikolas] Blitzen, this way.</i>

1:00:19.625 --> 1:00:21.833
<i>-[Truth Pixie] No, he's got me!</i>
<i>-Duck!</i>

1:00:22.375 --> 1:00:23.416
<i>[grunts]</i>

1:00:23.500 --> 1:00:25.291
<i>-Got him!</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] Nearly there!</i>

1:00:25.916 --> 1:00:27.833
<i>-Oh no.</i>
<i>-[guard 1] Got you now.</i>

1:00:27.916 --> 1:00:29.666
<i>-[guard 2] Get down!</i>
<i>-[guard 3] Get down!</i>

1:00:29.750 --> 1:00:31.500
<i>-[guard 4] We've cornered them all.</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

1:00:31.583 --> 1:00:32.708
<i>[guard 5] Form a circle.</i>

1:00:35.000 --> 1:00:38.083
<i>-[Truth Pixie] They're everywhere.</i>
<i>-That's it, lads. Tighten the noose!</i>

1:00:38.166 --> 1:00:40.250
<i>-[guard] Get down. Now!</i>
<i>-[Blitzen grunts]</i>

1:00:40.875 --> 1:00:43.708
<i>They have no idea</i>
<i>how exhausting being this powerful is.</i>

1:00:44.416 --> 1:00:45.541
<i>[Mop] </i>Stop!

1:00:46.666 --> 1:00:47.666
<i>Yes?</i>

1:00:48.208 --> 1:00:49.625
<i>Do they capture him?</i>

1:00:49.708 --> 1:00:51.666
<i>-I'm sorry?</i>
<i>-Does he die?</i>

1:00:51.750 --> 1:00:55.916
<i>-Stop now if that happens. Stop right now.</i>
<i>-We couldn't handle it.</i>

1:00:56.416 --> 1:00:57.833
<i>You could, you know.</i>

1:00:57.916 --> 1:01:03.416
<i>You can handle anything</i>
<i>because you've already handled everything.</i>

1:01:08.250 --> 1:01:10.750
<i>Nikolas was surrounded.</i>

1:01:10.833 --> 1:01:15.375
<i>Every direction they looked,</i>
<i>elves blocked their escape.</i>

1:01:16.291 --> 1:01:17.875
<i>I can't get caught again.</i>

1:01:17.958 --> 1:01:20.208
<i>Lucky for you,</i>
<i>I've got more tricks up my sleeve.</i>

1:01:20.291 --> 1:01:22.708
<i>And by tricks, I mean improvised</i>
<i>homemade explosives.</i>

1:01:22.791 --> 1:01:24.583
<i>-Wait, what?</i>
<i>-Well, grab them!</i>

1:01:25.166 --> 1:01:27.708
<i>[explosive whistling, whooshing]</i>

1:01:29.041 --> 1:01:30.625
<i>-Miika, cover your ears.</i>
<i>-Why?</i>

1:01:32.625 --> 1:01:34.583
<i>-[guard] Get down!</i>
<i>-[Mother Vodal grunts]</i>

1:01:34.666 --> 1:01:38.166
<i>-Blitzen, go!</i>
<i>-[guard] Watch out! They're right here!</i>

1:01:38.708 --> 1:01:40.375
<i>-[Nikolas grunts]</i>
<i>-[exploding]</i>

1:01:40.958 --> 1:01:43.791
<i>-Gates! Get the gates!</i>
<i>-[guard 1] Yes, Mother Vodal!</i>

1:01:45.875 --> 1:01:48.541
<i>-[guard 2] Stop!</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] We're not gonna make it.</i>

1:01:48.625 --> 1:01:50.291
<i>[grunting]</i>

1:01:50.375 --> 1:01:51.250
<i>What are you doing?</i>

1:01:52.041 --> 1:01:53.958
<i>-[Truth Pixie grunts]</i>
<i>-[clanging]</i>

1:01:54.041 --> 1:01:55.666
<i>I'll hold the gate. You go.</i>

1:01:55.750 --> 1:01:57.833
<i>-No, I can't go without you.</i>
<i>-We really can.</i>

1:01:57.916 --> 1:01:59.750
<i>-[Mother Vodal] Go!</i>
<i>-[guard] Forward.</i>

1:01:59.833 --> 1:02:03.083
<i>You should go.</i>
<i>This one's gonna be loud. [grunts]</i>

1:02:03.166 --> 1:02:05.291
<i>-[Truth Pixie chuckles]</i>
<i>-[Mother Vodal] Get them!</i>

1:02:05.375 --> 1:02:08.791
<i>-Go! Go! Find your father.</i>
<i>-[Blitzen grunts]</i>

1:02:09.375 --> 1:02:11.250
<i>[Mother Vodal] No! No! It's going to blow!</i>

1:02:13.083 --> 1:02:14.083
<i>[Blitzen bellows]</i>

1:02:18.791 --> 1:02:19.916
<i>[Truth Pixie laughing]</i>

1:02:20.750 --> 1:02:21.958
<i>[Mother Vodal screaming]</i>

1:02:22.583 --> 1:02:25.541
<i>-[Nikolas] Come on, Blitzen.</i>
<i>-[Mother Vodal] Don't let him go!</i>

1:02:25.625 --> 1:02:27.416
<i>Break it in, you fools!</i>

1:02:27.500 --> 1:02:29.000
<i>What are you doing?</i>

1:02:32.500 --> 1:02:34.500
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

1:02:45.291 --> 1:02:48.125
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>All day
the three friends searched

1:02:49.041 --> 1:02:54.833
<i>over mountains, and streams,</i>
<i>and lakes frozen solid.</i>

1:02:55.375 --> 1:02:56.458
<i>[Blitzen snorting]</i>

1:02:57.208 --> 1:02:59.791
<i>[Aunt Ruth]</i> Somewhere
in the vast wilderness,

1:03:00.708 --> 1:03:03.333
<i>Nikolas hoped to find his father</i>

1:03:04.708 --> 1:03:06.416
<i>and solve the mystery…</i>

1:03:06.500 --> 1:03:09.583
<i>-[Nikolas] Whoa, Blitzen.</i>
<i>-[Aunt Ruth] </i>…of the lost elf child.

1:03:11.125 --> 1:03:12.291
<i>[Nikolas grunts]</i>

1:03:12.375 --> 1:03:13.541
<i>[Blitzen bellows]</i>

1:03:14.708 --> 1:03:15.541
<i>Smoke.</i>

1:03:16.041 --> 1:03:18.041
<i>[wind whistling]</i>

1:03:21.458 --> 1:03:23.458
<i>[birds cawing]</i>

1:03:24.500 --> 1:03:25.666
<i>[fluttering]</i>

1:03:32.875 --> 1:03:34.250
<i>-Hey, Miika.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

1:03:34.333 --> 1:03:37.458
<i>-Look at this.</i>
<i>-Thread. Any idea where it leads?</i>

1:03:37.541 --> 1:03:40.416
<i>-No, but it's got to lead to somewhere.</i>
<i>-[Blitzen grunts]</i>

1:03:41.208 --> 1:03:42.500
<i>That's reassuring.</i>

1:03:43.583 --> 1:03:45.458
<i>[whooshing]</i>

1:03:45.541 --> 1:03:47.541
<i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

1:04:04.125 --> 1:04:06.125
<i>[Miika sniffing]</i>

1:04:07.625 --> 1:04:08.458
<i>Little Kip.</i>

1:04:12.500 --> 1:04:13.541
<i>[exhales sharply]</i>

1:04:14.208 --> 1:04:15.083
<i>[chain clinking]</i>

1:04:15.166 --> 1:04:17.375
<i>-[bird fluttering, cawing]</i>
<i>-[snow whooshing]</i>

1:04:18.833 --> 1:04:21.416
<i>I know you're scared. I am too.</i>

1:04:23.916 --> 1:04:24.916
<i>I'm here to help.</i>

1:04:33.875 --> 1:04:35.875
<i>[men laughing]</i>

1:04:37.875 --> 1:04:39.125
<i>[cawing]</i>

1:04:40.000 --> 1:04:42.500
<i>-[man 1] Easiest catch I've ever made.</i>
<i>-[man 2] I know.</i>

1:04:42.583 --> 1:04:45.083
<i>-[man 3] Just like catching a rabbit?</i>
<i>-[men laugh]</i>

1:04:45.875 --> 1:04:48.041
<i>-[Miika] Lots of birds here.</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] Shh.</i>

1:04:48.125 --> 1:04:50.125
<i>-[man] He is swift.</i>
<i>-[Miika] Just saying.</i>

1:04:52.208 --> 1:04:54.083
<i>[man 1] You've all</i>
<i>tasted a rabbit, I suspect.</i>

1:04:54.166 --> 1:04:56.500
<i>Depends which promise you want to keep,</i>

1:04:57.125 --> 1:05:01.166
<i>the one to your king</i>
<i>or the one to your son. [laughs]</i>

1:05:01.250 --> 1:05:02.875
<i>[men laughing]</i>

1:05:04.541 --> 1:05:05.750
<i>[man 2] It's not long now.</i>

1:05:06.375 --> 1:05:07.875
<i>You better be quiet or…</i>

1:05:08.791 --> 1:05:10.000
<i>-[bow squeaks]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas gasps]</i>

1:05:10.083 --> 1:05:13.833
<i>Don't move a muscle.</i>

1:05:15.166 --> 1:05:16.166
<i>Who are you?</i>

1:05:17.250 --> 1:05:18.833
<i>Tell me or you're dead.</i>

1:05:19.625 --> 1:05:23.000
<i>I'm just lost in the forest.</i>
<i>I'm not causing any trouble.</i>

1:05:23.083 --> 1:05:27.500
<i>You're up to something. Tell me what,</i>
<i>or I'll put an arrow through you.</i>

1:05:27.583 --> 1:05:29.583
<i>Hey, what's going on here?</i>

1:05:29.666 --> 1:05:31.791
<i>I found this boy wandering around.</i>

1:05:31.875 --> 1:05:35.125
<i>What are you doing here, boy? Who are you?</i>

1:05:35.208 --> 1:05:37.666
<i>-[man 1] What are you doing here?</i>
<i>-[man 2] Who are you, boy?</i>

1:05:37.750 --> 1:05:39.541
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-You're Joel's son.</i>

1:05:39.625 --> 1:05:41.791
<i>[Nikolas] My father. Where is he?</i>

1:05:41.875 --> 1:05:42.708
<i>Nikolas?</i>

1:05:44.583 --> 1:05:45.416
<i>It's you?</i>

1:05:46.708 --> 1:05:50.791
<i>-Papa. Papa.</i>
<i>-[sobbing]</i>

1:05:51.583 --> 1:05:52.791
<i>[Joel] How are you here?</i>

1:05:53.333 --> 1:05:55.750
<i>[Nikolas] I came to look for you. [sighs]</i>

1:05:57.083 --> 1:05:58.333
<i>[sniffles]</i>

1:05:58.958 --> 1:06:01.291
<i>You didn't tell me</i>
<i>you were kidnapping an elf.</i>

1:06:02.000 --> 1:06:04.250
<i>You said you were gonna find proof</i>
<i>of Elfhelm.</i>

1:06:04.750 --> 1:06:09.166
<i>Yeah, what could be better proof</i>
<i>than a real-life elf, eh?</i>

1:06:09.916 --> 1:06:14.416
<i>They must have made you do it, Papa.</i>
<i>Please tell me that's what happened.</i>

1:06:14.500 --> 1:06:17.041
<i>-It's for our own good, Nikolas.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

1:06:19.375 --> 1:06:23.125
<i>The king asked for hope.</i>
<i>What's hopeful about this?</i>

1:06:25.458 --> 1:06:27.583
<i>We can take the elf back to Elfhelm.</i>

1:06:29.458 --> 1:06:30.458
<i>Back to his home.</i>

1:06:31.333 --> 1:06:32.625
<i>The elves will be happy.</i>

1:06:33.583 --> 1:06:36.875
<i>They might even give you a reward.</i>
<i>All of you.</i>

1:06:36.958 --> 1:06:38.166
<i>[men laugh]</i>

1:06:40.333 --> 1:06:42.458
<i>Being good</i>
<i>is better than being rich, Papa.</i>

1:06:43.541 --> 1:06:44.791
<i>Better than anything.</i>

1:06:46.791 --> 1:06:48.250
<i>And if you've forgotten that…</i>

1:06:50.041 --> 1:06:51.208
<i>you've forgotten Mama.</i>

1:06:54.458 --> 1:06:56.125
<i>I'm getting you out of here, Kip.</i>

1:06:56.208 --> 1:06:58.791
<i>-That's it! That's it! You gotta talk--</i>
<i>-[rattling cage]</i>

1:06:58.875 --> 1:06:59.875
<i>Anders!</i>

1:07:00.416 --> 1:07:02.208
<i>-Joel, get out of the way.</i>
<i>-He's my son.</i>

1:07:02.291 --> 1:07:04.625
<i>He's trying to help the elf escape.</i>

1:07:06.791 --> 1:07:09.000
<i>-Then we'll tie him up too.</i>
<i>-Papa.</i>

1:07:09.083 --> 1:07:11.333
<i>-So tight he can't run anywhere.</i>
<i>-Papa!</i>

1:07:11.416 --> 1:07:13.875
<i>-Quiet!</i>
<i>-[dogs barking]</i>

1:07:15.083 --> 1:07:17.208
<i>Okay, fine. Tie him up.</i>

1:07:18.541 --> 1:07:22.125
<i>-Tie the reindeer up as well.</i>
<i>-Papa, what? Papa!</i>

1:07:23.083 --> 1:07:26.458
<i>[sobbing] Papa! Papa, please!</i>

1:07:27.583 --> 1:07:28.666
<i>Papa!</i>

1:07:31.291 --> 1:07:32.583
<i>[Blitzen bellowing]</i>

1:07:32.666 --> 1:07:34.041
<i>-[Nikolas] Blitzen!</i>
<i>-[man 1] Steady!</i>

1:07:34.125 --> 1:07:35.416
<i>-Easy!</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] Leave him alone!</i>

1:07:35.500 --> 1:07:37.500
<i>-[man 2] Get hold.</i>
<i>-[man 3] Hold it. Hold it.</i>

1:07:37.583 --> 1:07:39.375
<i>[huffing, grunting]</i>

1:07:41.000 --> 1:07:41.875
<i>[grunts]</i>

1:07:41.958 --> 1:07:44.458
<i>Hurt my friend,</i>
<i>and I'll bite your eyeball.</i>

1:07:46.250 --> 1:07:48.750
<i>You did it. You got him to talk!</i>

1:07:48.833 --> 1:07:51.416
<i>Yeah, he did. He's amazing.</i>

1:07:53.666 --> 1:07:57.083
<i>Don't look at me like that, son.</i>
<i>I'm doing my best.</i>

1:07:57.750 --> 1:07:58.833
<i>This is your best?</i>

1:07:59.750 --> 1:08:00.708
<i>I'll be honest with you.</i>

1:08:00.791 --> 1:08:03.416
<i>You can judge a person's character</i>
<i>if the first time you meet them,</i>

1:08:03.500 --> 1:08:05.583
<i>-they try and kill you with--</i>
<i>-Be quiet, Miika.</i>

1:08:05.666 --> 1:08:06.666
<i>An ax.</i>

1:08:08.083 --> 1:08:09.333
<i>[owl hooting]</i>

1:08:14.500 --> 1:08:16.500
<i>[snow whooshing]</i>

1:08:21.583 --> 1:08:23.583
<i>[Miika snoring]</i>

1:08:26.375 --> 1:08:27.375
<i>[soft thudding]</i>

1:08:32.291 --> 1:08:33.583
<i>[Nikolas exhales sharply]</i>

1:08:36.583 --> 1:08:37.666
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-Shh, shh.</i>

1:08:37.750 --> 1:08:40.583
<i>-[whispering] Stay calm. [grunts]</i>
<i>-What are you doing?</i>

1:08:42.625 --> 1:08:46.458
<i>-You're following me.</i>
<i>-[Miika] No. No. Why would we do that?</i>

1:08:46.541 --> 1:08:47.833
<i>Hey, Nikolas!</i>

1:08:49.500 --> 1:08:51.583
<i>[chain clinking]</i>

1:08:56.250 --> 1:08:59.791
<i>That was a terrible idea you had</i>
<i>coming here, running away, all of it.</i>

1:09:00.458 --> 1:09:04.083
<i>But you're my son,</i>
<i>and I'm on your side no matter what.</i>

1:09:04.750 --> 1:09:05.958
<i>Why are you smiling?</i>

1:09:06.833 --> 1:09:08.875
<i>There's goodness in you after all.</i>

1:09:09.875 --> 1:09:11.875
<i>[clicking]</i>

1:09:13.500 --> 1:09:14.875
<i>[Joel] Come on, Little Kip.</i>

1:09:23.583 --> 1:09:24.958
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-Here's the plan.</i>

1:09:25.041 --> 1:09:27.666
<i>I want you to take the reindeer</i>
<i>and get Kip back to Elfhelm.</i>

1:09:27.750 --> 1:09:30.333
<i>Then keep going south and don't stop</i>
<i>until you've reached the cabin.</i>

1:09:30.416 --> 1:09:31.791
<i>-[arrow whizzing]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

1:09:31.875 --> 1:09:34.333
<i>-[man 1] They're escaping.</i>
<i>-Go, go, go!</i>

1:09:34.416 --> 1:09:36.291
<i>-[man 1] They're getting away!</i>
<i>-[men yelling]</i>

1:09:36.375 --> 1:09:37.958
<i>-[man 2] Get up! Wake up, men!</i>
<i>-Nikolas.</i>

1:09:38.041 --> 1:09:39.833
<i>-[man 3] Hurry! Joel!</i>
<i>-Go, son!</i>

1:09:39.916 --> 1:09:41.583
<i>-Not without you.</i>
<i>-[man 4] Hurry up!</i>

1:09:41.666 --> 1:09:45.000
<i>Everybody up! Up, up, up!</i>
<i>Come on! Go, go, go!</i>

1:09:45.083 --> 1:09:47.250
<i>-They're escaping.</i>
<i>-[man 5] They've got the elf.</i>

1:09:47.333 --> 1:09:49.208
<i>Joel! Nikolas!</i>

1:09:49.291 --> 1:09:50.833
<i>I won't miss this time!</i>

1:09:52.291 --> 1:09:53.750
<i>Faster, Blitzen. Faster!</i>

1:09:57.625 --> 1:09:59.208
<i>-[man 1] Closer!</i>
<i>-[dogs barking]</i>

1:10:00.958 --> 1:10:02.958
<i>[man 2] Joel, we had a deal!</i>

1:10:03.041 --> 1:10:05.208
<i>[yelling]</i>

1:10:05.291 --> 1:10:07.291
<i>[arrows whizzing]</i>

1:10:08.041 --> 1:10:09.666
<i>[yelling]</i>

1:10:09.750 --> 1:10:11.708
<i>[man 3] Don't let them get away!</i>

1:10:12.791 --> 1:10:14.250
<i>[man 4] They're getting away!</i>

1:10:15.208 --> 1:10:17.541
<i>-[man 2] Run! Joel!</i>
<i>-[dogs barking]</i>

1:10:18.916 --> 1:10:20.125
<i>We've got to go faster!</i>

1:10:21.375 --> 1:10:23.458
<i>[dogs barking]</i>

1:10:26.416 --> 1:10:28.958
<i>-We're not going fast enough, Blitzen!</i>
<i>-[whooshing]</i>

1:10:29.750 --> 1:10:31.208
<i>[snorting]</i>

1:10:34.291 --> 1:10:36.041
<i>[grunting]</i>

1:10:36.791 --> 1:10:38.416
<i>[Joel] Nikolas, up ahead!</i>

1:10:40.541 --> 1:10:42.083
<i>[hoofs thundering]</i>

1:10:42.166 --> 1:10:44.166
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:10:48.791 --> 1:10:50.791
<i>[dogs barking]</i>

1:10:55.250 --> 1:10:58.000
<i>-Come on, Blitzen! There's magic in you!</i>
<i>-[whooshing]</i>

1:10:58.083 --> 1:10:59.166
<i>[bellows]</i>

1:10:59.250 --> 1:11:02.125
<i>That's it, boy! You're doing it!</i>

1:11:04.458 --> 1:11:05.916
<i>I'm weighing you down!</i>

1:11:06.000 --> 1:11:08.833
<i>[Nikolas] We're nearly there!</i>
<i>Go on, Blitzen!</i>

1:11:10.875 --> 1:11:13.750
<i>Please, fly, Blitzen! Fly!</i>

1:11:16.375 --> 1:11:18.625
<i>-No, Papa!</i>
<i>-I love you, Nikolas.</i>

1:11:18.708 --> 1:11:21.125
<i>-No, Papa!</i>
<i>-You have so much good to give.</i>

1:11:21.208 --> 1:11:22.791
<i>It's better than anything.</i>

1:11:22.875 --> 1:11:24.166
<i>[Nikolas] No, Papa!</i>

1:11:26.416 --> 1:11:28.416
<i>[rumbling]</i>

1:11:33.958 --> 1:11:36.625
<i>Papa, no! Papa!</i>

1:11:37.250 --> 1:11:38.375
<i>Papa, please!</i>

1:11:38.458 --> 1:11:42.666
<i>Papa, no! Papa, no!</i>

1:11:42.750 --> 1:11:46.000
<i>Papa! Papa!</i>

1:11:46.083 --> 1:11:48.083
<i>[sobbing]</i>

1:11:49.333 --> 1:11:50.291
<i>Papa.</i>

1:11:51.250 --> 1:11:52.625
<i>[sobbing]</i>

1:11:56.833 --> 1:11:57.791
<i>Papa.</i>

1:11:57.875 --> 1:11:59.083
<i>[sobbing]</i>

1:12:07.833 --> 1:12:08.666
<i>[slurping]</i>

1:12:08.750 --> 1:12:12.833
<i>-That's the worst story I've ever heard.</i>
<i>-Well, I haven't finished.</i>

1:12:12.916 --> 1:12:15.458
<i>There's no way you can get to</i>
<i>happy ending from here.</i>

1:12:15.541 --> 1:12:16.833
<i>I don't have to.</i>

1:12:16.916 --> 1:12:21.250
<i>Happiness isn't compulsory,</i>
<i>and… and nothing ever ends.</i>

1:12:21.333 --> 1:12:24.083
<i>Well, Merry Christmas, everyone.</i>

1:12:24.166 --> 1:12:25.500
<i>[Mop] But, Aunt Ruth?</i>

1:12:26.583 --> 1:12:27.833
<i>What is it, Moppet?</i>

1:12:29.250 --> 1:12:30.958
<i>Poor Nikolas.</i>

1:12:33.375 --> 1:12:38.625
<i>I know. The pain he felt was incredible.</i>

1:12:38.708 --> 1:12:40.708
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

1:12:40.791 --> 1:12:42.791
<i>[wind whooshing]</i>

1:12:46.208 --> 1:12:49.458
<i>[Aunt  Ruth] </i>Grief is
the price we pay for love,

1:12:51.208 --> 1:12:54.916
<i>and worth it a million times over.</i>

1:13:03.500 --> 1:13:04.333
<i>Nikolas…</i>

1:13:07.041 --> 1:13:08.041
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

1:13:10.958 --> 1:13:15.208
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>But now, the time had come
for Nikolas to make things right

1:13:16.625 --> 1:13:22.333
<i>and bring Little Kip back home to Elfhelm.</i>

1:13:22.416 --> 1:13:24.750
<i>-[motivational music playing]</i>
<i>-[Blitzen grunts]</i>

1:13:38.333 --> 1:13:40.333
<i>[grunting, chuffing]</i>

1:13:45.166 --> 1:13:46.166
<i>Listen.</i>

1:13:47.875 --> 1:13:50.375
<i>I know you must think my father</i>
<i>was a bad human,</i>

1:13:51.416 --> 1:13:52.583
<i>but there's good too.</i>

1:13:55.250 --> 1:13:56.625
<i>Humans are complicated.</i>

1:13:57.166 --> 1:13:58.666
<i>[breathes deeply]</i>

1:14:03.416 --> 1:14:06.958
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Nikolas found
Elfhelm's streets deserted.

1:14:07.625 --> 1:14:09.791
<i>-Not an elf in sight.</i>
-[staff thudding]

1:14:10.458 --> 1:14:12.125
<i>-[loud thud]</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

1:14:12.208 --> 1:14:16.333
<i>Mother Harkers,</i>
<i>for heinous crimes against elf kind,</i>

1:14:16.416 --> 1:14:19.375
<i>you are herewith banished for life.</i>

1:14:19.458 --> 1:14:20.708
<i>You can punish us,</i>

1:14:20.791 --> 1:14:26.333
<i>but you can never take away the ground</i>
<i>on which we stand.</i>

1:14:28.375 --> 1:14:30.375
<i>-[whooshing]</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

1:14:34.208 --> 1:14:36.375
<i>-[staff thuds]</i>
<i>-This is our home.</i>

1:14:36.458 --> 1:14:37.583
<i>[Mother Vodal] Enough!</i>

1:14:38.958 --> 1:14:41.458
<i>Banished! You're all banished.</i>

1:14:41.541 --> 1:14:42.833
<i>You can't do this.</i>

1:14:42.916 --> 1:14:44.333
<i>[Mother Vodal] I just have.</i>

1:14:44.416 --> 1:14:49.166
<i>We can't have you here threatening</i>
<i>our safety, disrupting our lives.</i>

1:14:50.875 --> 1:14:54.708
<i>Have we already forgotten</i>
<i>the lessons of poor Little Kip?</i>

1:14:54.791 --> 1:14:56.083
<i>[door opens]</i>

1:14:56.166 --> 1:14:58.916
<i>-Why don't you ask him yourself?</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

1:14:59.000 --> 1:15:00.083
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:15:03.416 --> 1:15:05.333
<i>[elves murmuring]</i>

1:15:06.458 --> 1:15:07.458
<i>[elves gasp]</i>

1:15:29.250 --> 1:15:32.166
<i>I'm not going to make a big speech.</i>

1:15:36.000 --> 1:15:38.000
<i>[elf coughing]</i>

1:15:40.375 --> 1:15:42.291
<i>[smacks lips] Well, I guess that's it.</i>

1:15:44.291 --> 1:15:46.208
<i>If Little Kip is alive…</i>

1:15:48.416 --> 1:15:52.458
<i>well, then… hope is alive.</i>

1:15:52.541 --> 1:15:55.083
<i>-[elf] Thank goodness.</i>
<i>-[all applauding]</i>

1:15:58.500 --> 1:15:59.500
<i>[Mother Vodal] Wait.</i>

1:16:00.875 --> 1:16:02.583
<i>Put him down. Bring him back.</i>

1:16:06.125 --> 1:16:07.291
<i>Hip hip for Kip!</i>

1:16:07.375 --> 1:16:09.916
<i>Adapt. Adapt. We must adapt.</i>

1:16:10.000 --> 1:16:13.041
<i>-Wait! I command you!</i>
<i>-[cheering]</i>

1:16:13.125 --> 1:16:15.125
<i>[victorious music playing]</i>

1:16:20.750 --> 1:16:21.916
<i>[whooshing]</i>

1:16:36.833 --> 1:16:37.958
<i>[knocking on door]</i>

1:16:38.833 --> 1:16:39.708
<i>[clears throat]</i>

1:16:40.791 --> 1:16:43.875
<i>-What did he say?</i>
<i>-Nothing yet. He just knocked.</i>

1:16:45.625 --> 1:16:46.958
<i>Still exciting though.</i>

1:16:47.041 --> 1:16:48.208
<i>[bell dinging]</i>

1:16:55.000 --> 1:16:56.166
<i>Wha…</i>

1:16:57.208 --> 1:16:58.041
<i>What is it?</i>

1:17:01.666 --> 1:17:03.291
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:17:03.875 --> 1:17:05.500
<i>Oh, my baby!</i>

1:17:05.583 --> 1:17:07.083
<i>[all cheering, applauding]</i>

1:17:11.708 --> 1:17:13.083
<i>I am sorry, Mum.</i>

1:17:13.166 --> 1:17:16.375
<i>Yes, we'll talk about that</i>
<i>when your father comes home.</i>

1:17:23.166 --> 1:17:24.500
<i>You found your father, didn't you?</i>

1:17:27.958 --> 1:17:30.041
<i>[sighs] Listen.</i>

1:17:30.791 --> 1:17:35.708
<i>[inhales] The only thing in life</i>
<i>that is simple and clear is the truth.</i>

1:17:37.375 --> 1:17:38.750
<i>But it can be painful.</i>

1:17:42.750 --> 1:17:44.166
<i>Does the pain ever go away?</i>

1:17:44.250 --> 1:17:45.250
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:17:46.666 --> 1:17:47.541
<i>No.</i>

1:17:49.291 --> 1:17:50.708
<i>You couldn't just lie once?</i>

1:17:51.333 --> 1:17:54.000
<i>But you learn to live with it.</i>

1:17:54.666 --> 1:17:56.750
<i>And you get stronger because of it.</i>

1:17:57.708 --> 1:18:00.000
<i>And that's the truth. [chuckles]</i>

1:18:03.125 --> 1:18:04.375
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

1:18:05.375 --> 1:18:08.750
<i>[Father Topo] I don't fully understand</i>
<i>how you actually did it.</i>

1:18:09.541 --> 1:18:11.291
<i>Take me through it from the--</i>

1:18:12.250 --> 1:18:13.458
<i>You saved our child.</i>

1:18:14.458 --> 1:18:17.375
<i>-Anyone could have done it.</i>
<i>-But only you did.</i>

1:18:17.458 --> 1:18:19.250
<i>Don't be a hero. Take the win.</i>

1:18:19.333 --> 1:18:21.291
<i>We are simple top makers.</i>

1:18:21.375 --> 1:18:24.291
<i>He's being humble.</i>
<i>Their tops are top-notch.</i>

1:18:25.000 --> 1:18:26.166
<i>To show our appreciation,</i>

1:18:26.250 --> 1:18:29.291
<i>we'd like to offer you a selection</i>
<i>of our finest wares.</i>

1:18:33.375 --> 1:18:34.666
<i>I only ever had one toy.</i>

1:18:37.708 --> 1:18:38.958
<i>It was a turnip doll.</i>

1:18:39.666 --> 1:18:42.333
<i>-My mama made it for me.</i>
<i>-It's a very sad story.</i>

1:18:43.000 --> 1:18:45.208
<i>-He ate it.</i>
<i>-We've all done things we regret.</i>

1:18:45.291 --> 1:18:46.416
<i>Only one toy.</i>

1:18:47.166 --> 1:18:49.791
<i>Playing with it</i>
<i>made me feel happy and loved.</i>

1:18:50.791 --> 1:18:52.750
<i>It's more than any one kid needs.</i>

1:18:58.458 --> 1:19:00.291
<i>-Wait.</i>
<i>-What is it?</i>

1:19:00.916 --> 1:19:03.250
<i>Could you make more? Lots, lots more.</i>

1:19:03.333 --> 1:19:05.000
<i>-Of course--</i>
<i>-We'll need anything you have.</i>

1:19:05.083 --> 1:19:07.666
<i>Shiny things,</i>
<i>stacking things, things that wind up.</i>

1:19:07.750 --> 1:19:11.875
<i>-I'll need to borrow this curtain too.</i>
<i>-Could you be kidnapping another elf?</i>

1:19:11.958 --> 1:19:15.416
<i>-No, bigger. Much, much bigger.</i>
<i>-We're opening a curtain shop?</i>

1:19:15.500 --> 1:19:18.458
<i>-[Father Topo] Right. Come on.</i>
<i>-And we haven't much time!</i>

1:19:18.541 --> 1:19:22.791
<i>-And I haven't much cheese.</i>
<i>-Why didn't you say so? I make my own.</i>

1:19:22.875 --> 1:19:23.916
<i>Marry me.</i>

1:19:24.000 --> 1:19:26.000
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

1:19:45.000 --> 1:19:47.000
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

1:19:50.500 --> 1:19:53.875
<i>[Miika] It's all right, everyone.</i>
<i>I'm powering the wheel. [grunting]</i>

1:19:56.541 --> 1:19:58.541
<i>[tools clanking]</i>

1:20:02.916 --> 1:20:04.708
<i>[elf] And the wheel is on the side.</i>

1:20:07.625 --> 1:20:09.625
<i>-Thank you. It's perfect.</i>
<i>-[elf] Bring the wheels.</i>

1:20:09.708 --> 1:20:13.000
<i>That's it, everyone. You're doing great.</i>
<i>Keep up the good work.</i>

1:20:13.625 --> 1:20:14.833
<i>Amazing. Thank you.</i>

1:20:15.541 --> 1:20:17.791
<i>Missed a spot. Try again.</i>

1:20:19.291 --> 1:20:20.458
<i>I've… I've seen worse.</i>

1:20:38.916 --> 1:20:40.250
<i>[rattling]</i>

1:21:00.291 --> 1:21:01.625
<i>[chuckling]</i>

1:21:04.416 --> 1:21:06.708
<i>[inhales, blows]</i>

1:21:06.791 --> 1:21:09.416
<i>-Thank you.</i>
<i>-I wish you could see this, Mama.</i>

1:21:10.500 --> 1:21:13.000
<i>It's everything you hoped for.</i>

1:21:14.083 --> 1:21:16.291
<i>It's a five-minute warning, everyone.</i>

1:21:16.916 --> 1:21:19.083
<i>-Five minutes!</i>
<i>-Freshly painted.</i>

1:21:19.166 --> 1:21:20.750
<i>Blue for peace,</i>

1:21:20.833 --> 1:21:22.041
<i>red for joy,</i>

1:21:22.125 --> 1:21:25.291
<i>green for wonder, and yellow because</i>
<i>it makes my eyes tickle.</i>

1:21:25.375 --> 1:21:26.291
<i>Do you like it?</i>

1:21:26.375 --> 1:21:27.625
<i>Is it a bit garish?</i>

1:21:28.750 --> 1:21:30.333
<i>-I think it's perfect.</i>
<i>-Love it.</i>

1:21:30.416 --> 1:21:32.625
<i>That reindeer's not going to drive itself.</i>

1:21:32.708 --> 1:21:35.750
<i>All right, everyone, it's time.</i>
<i>We haven't got long.</i>

1:21:36.875 --> 1:21:38.875
<i>[ticking]</i>

1:21:40.125 --> 1:21:42.125
<i>[clicking, whirring]</i>

1:21:45.583 --> 1:21:47.291
<i>[elf 1] Merry Christmas!</i>

1:21:48.208 --> 1:21:50.208
<i>[elf 2] Merry Christmas!</i>

1:21:52.083 --> 1:21:54.458
<i>-[Father Topo] Here, take this.</i>
<i>-No, I couldn't.</i>

1:21:54.541 --> 1:21:56.250
<i>You're one of us now.</i>

1:21:57.583 --> 1:22:01.875
<i>We can't have you representing Elfhelm</i>
<i>dressed all shoddily, can we?</i>

1:22:01.958 --> 1:22:04.416
<i>-[Miika chuckles]</i>
<i>-They look up to you, you know.</i>

1:22:05.666 --> 1:22:06.625
<i>We all do.</i>

1:22:07.541 --> 1:22:10.625
<i>And not just because you're</i>
<i>so freakishly tall.</i>

1:22:10.708 --> 1:22:11.750
<i>-Ha!</i>
<i>-[sniffles]</i>

1:22:13.291 --> 1:22:16.291
<i>Go on. Elfhelm's your home now.</i>

1:22:16.958 --> 1:22:19.000
<i>Get out there. Make us proud.</i>

1:22:22.041 --> 1:22:23.958
<i>[grunts] This is it.</i>

1:22:24.041 --> 1:22:26.125
<i>-Thanks for everything.</i>
<i>-[Father Topo] Fly safely.</i>

1:22:27.083 --> 1:22:29.208
<i>We got it from here. See you soon.</i>

1:22:29.291 --> 1:22:30.666
<i>[Father Topo] We're counting on it.</i>

1:22:31.208 --> 1:22:33.125
<i>-Stop!</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

1:22:33.708 --> 1:22:34.833
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

1:22:35.541 --> 1:22:37.166
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[elves gasp]</i>

1:22:37.250 --> 1:22:38.708
<i>[all gasp]</i>

1:22:39.375 --> 1:22:42.208
<i>That human must not be allowed</i>
<i>to leave Elfhelm.</i>

1:22:44.083 --> 1:22:46.291
<i>-[whooshes]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

1:22:48.291 --> 1:22:50.541
<i>So he bought us back the little elf child.</i>

1:22:50.625 --> 1:22:51.958
<i>[whimpering]</i>

1:22:52.625 --> 1:22:54.041
<i>Hooray for that.</i>

1:22:55.583 --> 1:22:59.750
<i>But what is one boy when held against</i>
<i>an entire community?</i>

1:22:59.833 --> 1:23:00.958
<i>[groaning]</i>

1:23:02.166 --> 1:23:04.416
<i>[Mother Vodal] We must not allow</i>
<i>what we have gained</i>

1:23:04.500 --> 1:23:07.083
<i>to make us blind to what we may lose.</i>

1:23:07.166 --> 1:23:08.166
<i>Our home.</i>

1:23:09.666 --> 1:23:10.541
<i>Our culture.</i>

1:23:10.625 --> 1:23:12.166
<i>[whooshing]</i>

1:23:20.916 --> 1:23:22.000
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:23:26.833 --> 1:23:27.833
<i>[exhales sharply]</i>

1:23:30.833 --> 1:23:31.875
<i>No, it can't be..</i>

1:23:36.708 --> 1:23:37.708
<i>Uh-uh.</i>

1:23:38.875 --> 1:23:40.333
<i>[whooshing]</i>

1:23:46.375 --> 1:23:47.458
<i>Boy…</i>

1:23:50.541 --> 1:23:52.166
<i>…where did you get that pendant?</i>

1:23:56.208 --> 1:23:57.375
<i>Where did you get that?</i>

1:24:01.958 --> 1:24:02.833
<i>My mother.</i>

1:24:05.041 --> 1:24:06.333
<i>She wore it all her life.</i>

1:24:11.083 --> 1:24:12.583
<i>[exhales]</i>

1:24:16.583 --> 1:24:18.541
<i>I never thought I'd see it again.</i>

1:24:21.708 --> 1:24:22.750
<i>Long ago…</i>

1:24:26.541 --> 1:24:28.875
<i>a human girl wandered into our village…</i>

1:24:31.416 --> 1:24:32.708
<i>tired and lost.</i>

1:24:35.625 --> 1:24:37.291
<i>We took her in.</i>

1:24:38.250 --> 1:24:43.916
<i>She was loving and kind and full of hope.</i>

1:24:46.916 --> 1:24:48.416
<i>She became our friend…</i>

1:24:53.708 --> 1:24:54.708
<i>my friend…</i>

1:24:57.875 --> 1:25:02.791
<i>until the day the snows melted,</i>
<i>and she returned to her home in the South.</i>

1:25:04.500 --> 1:25:06.208
<i>Her pockets full of chocolates.</i>

1:25:07.125 --> 1:25:08.125
<i>Hmm.</i>

1:25:10.375 --> 1:25:13.375
<i>That's where</i>
<i>all my chocolates went. [chuckles]</i>

1:25:14.791 --> 1:25:18.541
<i>As I recall, Dimelza,</i>

1:25:20.166 --> 1:25:24.416
<i>there was a time</i>
<i>you loved humans more than most.</i>

1:25:26.791 --> 1:25:30.208
<i>-But she left without a word.</i>
<i>-[Nikolas] She never did forget.</i>

1:25:32.666 --> 1:25:35.625
<i>My mother told me the story</i>
<i>of Elfhelm every night.</i>

1:25:37.333 --> 1:25:38.708
<i>It was always with her.</i>

1:25:39.416 --> 1:25:40.583
<i>[inhales sharply]</i>

1:25:42.708 --> 1:25:43.708
<i>Lumi.</i>

1:25:49.916 --> 1:25:51.083
<i>We called her Lumi.</i>

1:25:51.583 --> 1:25:52.583
<i>[chuckling] Lumi.</i>

1:25:56.750 --> 1:26:00.458
<i>The girl who came, but couldn't stay long.</i>

1:26:04.708 --> 1:26:05.708
<i>I see her.</i>

1:26:08.708 --> 1:26:10.208
<i>I can see her in you.</i>

1:26:13.166 --> 1:26:15.083
<i>[sobs]</i>

1:26:17.000 --> 1:26:18.625
<i>[Nikolas] My mother told me Elfhelm</i>

1:26:19.125 --> 1:26:22.291
<i>was the most hopeful,</i>
<i>happiest place in the world.</i>

1:26:24.375 --> 1:26:27.625
<i>And it should be that again,</i>
<i>especially on Christmas.</i>

1:26:32.750 --> 1:26:33.916
<i>The day she named me after.</i>

1:26:35.166 --> 1:26:36.250
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:26:37.666 --> 1:26:38.666
<i>She called you…</i>

1:26:42.125 --> 1:26:43.750
<i>She called you Christmas.</i>

1:26:45.333 --> 1:26:46.416
<i>[chuckles]</i>

1:26:47.000 --> 1:26:50.208
<i>[Father Topo] We still have some time</i>
<i>before the big day.</i>

1:26:52.083 --> 1:26:54.875
<i>We could make it the best one ever.</i>

1:26:56.458 --> 1:26:58.500
<i>-[chuffing]</i>
<i>-Ready, old friend?</i>

1:26:58.583 --> 1:26:59.833
<i>Born ready.</i>

1:27:02.125 --> 1:27:03.708
<i>You meant the reindeer, didn't you?</i>

1:27:03.791 --> 1:27:05.333
<i>[elves cheering]</i>

1:27:05.416 --> 1:27:07.166
<i>[Nikolas] Faster, Blitzen, faster!</i>

1:27:09.833 --> 1:27:11.333
<i>[Blitzen snorting]</i>

1:27:12.500 --> 1:27:14.458
<i>[Truth Pixie] See you soon, friend!</i>

1:27:15.375 --> 1:27:17.416
<i>Happy flying, Father Christmas!</i>

1:27:17.500 --> 1:27:19.500
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

1:27:33.000 --> 1:27:35.000
<i>[Miika laughing]</i>

1:27:40.833 --> 1:27:42.708
<i>[Nikolas] There, Blitzen! Down there!</i>

1:27:42.791 --> 1:27:44.791
<i>[wind howling]</i>

1:27:52.500 --> 1:27:53.666
<i>[snarling]</i>

1:27:53.750 --> 1:27:55.750
<i>[creaking]</i>

1:27:56.458 --> 1:27:58.458
<i>[grunting softly]</i>

1:27:59.125 --> 1:28:00.166
<i>[Nikolas grunts]</i>

1:28:01.916 --> 1:28:03.166
<i>-[snorts]</i>
<i>-[Nikolas yells]</i>

1:28:03.250 --> 1:28:04.208
<i>[Miika groans]</i>

1:28:04.833 --> 1:28:05.666
<i>Hmm?</i>

1:28:05.750 --> 1:28:07.375
<i>[Miika] I think I bent my tail.</i>

1:28:07.458 --> 1:28:08.291
<i>Who are you?</i>

1:28:10.541 --> 1:28:11.666
<i>What's in that bag?</i>

1:28:13.291 --> 1:28:16.291
<i>Hope and magic and wonder.</i>

1:28:16.958 --> 1:28:17.833
<i>Guards!</i>

1:28:17.916 --> 1:28:22.666
<i>Wait, the thing you've been searching for,</i>
<i>the discovery that can relight the spark.</i>

1:28:22.750 --> 1:28:23.750
<i>Oh that.</i>

1:28:25.291 --> 1:28:27.333
<i>I've pretty much given up on that.</i>

1:28:28.375 --> 1:28:32.083
<i>You see enough horses with horns stuck</i>
<i>to their head, you get a little cynical.</i>

1:28:32.166 --> 1:28:33.083
<i>Wait.</i>

1:28:33.166 --> 1:28:34.250
<i>Guards!</i>

1:28:34.875 --> 1:28:35.875
<i>Stop saying that.</i>

1:28:35.958 --> 1:28:37.875
<i>I don't think</i>
<i>there's anyone's there anyway.</i>

1:28:37.958 --> 1:28:39.708
<i>Just have a look, please.</i>

1:28:41.041 --> 1:28:42.250
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

1:28:42.333 --> 1:28:44.666
<i>All right, fine. Show me.</i>

1:28:47.125 --> 1:28:48.250
<i>[exhales]</i>

1:28:59.166 --> 1:29:00.250
<i>[King] Hmm.</i>

1:29:01.666 --> 1:29:03.333
<i>It's not very magical.</i>

1:29:07.250 --> 1:29:08.458
<i>How does it work?</i>

1:29:08.958 --> 1:29:10.958
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

1:29:12.666 --> 1:29:14.458
<i>[whimpering]</i>

1:29:16.375 --> 1:29:19.458
<i>Oh. [laughs]</i>

1:29:21.291 --> 1:29:22.708
<i>[Nikolas] We'll start there.</i>

1:29:22.791 --> 1:29:23.958
<i>[music continues]</i>

1:29:28.208 --> 1:29:29.041
<i>Hmm.</i>

1:29:35.708 --> 1:29:37.041
<i>Do kings give leg ups?</i>

1:29:38.416 --> 1:29:39.791
<i>[King] This one does.</i>

1:29:45.125 --> 1:29:46.500
<i>[rumbling, thud]</i>

1:29:59.666 --> 1:30:01.000
<i>[whispering] How did you get in?</i>

1:30:03.125 --> 1:30:04.958
<i>-What now?</i>
<i>-Watch.</i>

1:30:21.625 --> 1:30:23.208
<i>[King] Ho, ho, ho!</i>

1:30:40.291 --> 1:30:44.833
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>Nikolas showed the king
that it's not about the presents.

1:30:47.125 --> 1:30:49.041
<i>Although they are wonderful.</i>

1:30:53.333 --> 1:30:55.458
<i>It's about what's behind them.</i>

1:30:56.083 --> 1:30:57.333
<i>[whispering] Here's one.</i>

1:30:59.458 --> 1:31:03.291
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>We give what we have
to show that we care.

1:31:04.708 --> 1:31:05.750
<i>Hmm.</i>

1:31:07.625 --> 1:31:10.416
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>And then
we all share in the joy.

1:31:11.708 --> 1:31:12.708
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:31:18.541 --> 1:31:19.500
<i>[goose honking]</i>

1:31:19.583 --> 1:31:23.500
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>And that joy
can grow into hope

1:31:24.791 --> 1:31:30.125
<i>one house at a time</i>
<i>and spread throughout the land.</i>

1:31:30.208 --> 1:31:32.000
<i>I asked for something new.</i>

1:31:32.625 --> 1:31:35.833
<i>You've brought me something</i>
<i>we'd forgotten we already had.</i>

1:31:36.583 --> 1:31:37.416
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:31:37.958 --> 1:31:40.458
<i>-Well, good luck with it all.</i>
<i>-[Miika] Cheers.</i>

1:31:42.708 --> 1:31:45.833
<i>-Where do you think you're going?</i>
<i>-My work here is done. So…</i>

1:31:45.916 --> 1:31:47.375
<i>Done? Done?</i>

1:31:47.458 --> 1:31:50.541
<i>I've given you the idea.</i>
<i>I've shown you how it works.</i>

1:31:51.333 --> 1:31:54.000
<i>-So now I must appoint someone to run it.</i>
<i>-Great.</i>

1:31:54.500 --> 1:31:56.250
<i>Great. When can you start?</i>

1:31:58.125 --> 1:32:00.083
<i>I hardly know you, but it seems to me</i>

1:32:00.166 --> 1:32:04.458
<i>that if anyone deserves the infinite joy</i>
<i>of loving and being loved,</i>

1:32:04.541 --> 1:32:06.125
<i>it's you, my young friend.</i>

1:32:07.208 --> 1:32:09.541
<i>Besides, it's just just one day a year.</i>

1:32:10.625 --> 1:32:11.958
<i>What shall we call it?</i>

1:32:12.458 --> 1:32:16.125
<i>That's easy.</i>
<i>Nikolas and Miika the talking mouse day.</i>

1:32:18.291 --> 1:32:19.750
<i>Any other ideas?</i>

1:32:19.833 --> 1:32:21.833
<i>[hoofs thundering]</i>

1:32:21.916 --> 1:32:23.916
<i>[orchestral music playing]</i>

1:32:28.833 --> 1:32:30.250
<i>[Blitzen bellows]</i>

1:32:30.333 --> 1:32:32.541
<i>You know who else could use</i>
<i>some magic to believe in?</i>

1:32:32.625 --> 1:32:33.625
<i>Who?</i>

1:32:34.208 --> 1:32:37.041
<i>-[Aunt Carlotta] Bandit!</i>
<i>-[King] Come on!</i>

1:32:37.125 --> 1:32:39.291
<i>-[Aunt Carlotta] Bandit!</i>
<i>-[Nikolas grunts]</i>

1:32:39.375 --> 1:32:41.416
<i>-Intruder!</i>
<i>-[King] Let's go!</i>

1:32:41.500 --> 1:32:42.958
<i>[Aunt Carlotta gasps]</i>

1:32:43.750 --> 1:32:45.375
<i>[Nikolas] Hey, Aunt Carlotta!</i>

1:32:45.458 --> 1:32:47.208
<i>It's me, Nikolas.</i>

1:32:47.291 --> 1:32:50.125
<i>I'm flying on a reindeer,</i>
<i>and my mouse talks now.</i>

1:32:50.208 --> 1:32:51.083
<i>Ta-da!</i>

1:32:51.166 --> 1:32:54.583
<i>-And look, we brought our mate, the King.</i>
<i>-Hello!</i>

1:32:55.541 --> 1:32:57.416
<i>-Hi.</i>
<i>-[Blitzen grunts]</i>

1:32:57.500 --> 1:33:01.125
<i>I just came back</i>
<i>to tell you magic is real.</i>

1:33:01.208 --> 1:33:02.875
<i>It is. It really is.</i>

1:33:03.500 --> 1:33:07.250
<i>-[whispering] Pocket.</i>
<i>-Oh yeah, check your pocket.</i>

1:33:08.041 --> 1:33:09.375
<i>[Aunt Carlotta] Oh.</i>

1:33:09.458 --> 1:33:10.583
<i>[King laughs]</i>

1:33:18.166 --> 1:33:19.750
<i>Thank you, Nikolas!</i>

1:33:22.833 --> 1:33:25.583
<i>[Aunt Ruth] </i>The sack
was nearly empty of toys,

1:33:25.666 --> 1:33:30.208
<i>but for Nikolas,</i>
<i>the adventure was just beginning.</i>

1:33:32.916 --> 1:33:35.416
<i>And so it was that a king,</i>

1:33:36.125 --> 1:33:37.416
<i>a mouse,</i>

1:33:37.500 --> 1:33:38.500
<i>a reindeer,</i>

1:33:39.250 --> 1:33:41.166
<i>and a boy called Christmas</i>

1:33:41.958 --> 1:33:45.625
<i>disappeared back into the sky.</i>

1:33:48.000 --> 1:33:49.333
<i>I don't get it.</i>

1:33:49.416 --> 1:33:50.791
<i>Maybe next year.</i>

1:33:50.875 --> 1:33:54.500
<i>-Come on. It's simple. Use the--</i>
<i>-Wait, wait, I can figure it out.</i>

1:34:00.375 --> 1:34:01.708
<i>-I've got it.</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

1:34:02.791 --> 1:34:03.666
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:34:03.750 --> 1:34:04.833
<i>[switch clicks]</i>

1:34:04.916 --> 1:34:08.875
<i>[exhales] Can we have</i>
<i>another story again soon?</i>

1:34:08.958 --> 1:34:11.750
<i>Mmm, well, anytime you need one.</i>

1:34:11.833 --> 1:34:14.583
<i>-How about tomorrow?</i>
<i>-[laughs]</i>

1:34:17.000 --> 1:34:20.833
<i>Hey, what are you guys doing up?</i>
<i>It's way past your bedtime.</i>

1:34:20.916 --> 1:34:23.625
<i>I think next year we can let</i>
<i>Father Christmas do his thing.</i>

1:34:23.708 --> 1:34:26.541
<i>-Okay. Well, how about--</i>
<i>-Dad.</i>

1:34:26.625 --> 1:34:28.750
<i>[fire crackling]</i>

1:34:28.833 --> 1:34:30.833
<i>[gentle music playing]</i>

1:34:37.666 --> 1:34:38.666
<i>[Dad] I didn't--</i>

1:34:44.833 --> 1:34:46.791
<i>-I didn't--</i>
<i>-It's always the way.</i>

1:34:47.875 --> 1:34:49.791
<i>The darkest night will end.</i>

1:34:51.166 --> 1:34:55.625
<i>The sun will rise,</i>
<i>and Christmas mornings will come again</i>

1:34:55.708 --> 1:34:59.125
<i>when anything and everything can happen.</i>

1:34:59.208 --> 1:35:01.416
<i>-[Dad] I--</i>
<i>-[Aunt Ruth chuckles]</i>

1:35:04.250 --> 1:35:06.125
<i>Mommy would have loved this.</i>

1:35:07.916 --> 1:35:10.083
<i>She's never gonna come back, is she?</i>

1:35:12.166 --> 1:35:16.375
<i>No, but you are the best memory</i>
<i>of her now.</i>

1:35:17.166 --> 1:35:19.166
<i>[inspirational music playing]</i>

1:35:37.458 --> 1:35:39.333
<i>-[girl] Aunt Ruth.</i>
<i>-Yes?</i>

1:35:39.416 --> 1:35:41.916
<i>Is that really how Christmas</i>
<i>properly began?</i>

1:35:43.333 --> 1:35:47.166
<i>Oh, it must be, it must be.</i>
<i>You see, I never lie.</i>

1:35:49.291 --> 1:35:50.291
<i>[door closes]</i>

1:35:51.541 --> 1:35:53.541
<i>-[festive music playing]</i>
<i>-[rattling]</i>

1:36:07.041 --> 1:36:09.500
<i>[sighs] Mm-hmm.</i>

1:36:13.708 --> 1:36:15.791
<i>[click, crackling]</i>

1:36:21.375 --> 1:36:23.375
<i>[whistling, bursting]</i>

1:36:24.291 --> 1:36:26.291
<i>[festive music playing]</i>

1:37:31.250 --> 1:37:33.250
<i>[music continues]</i>

1:38:24.916 --> 1:38:26.916
<i>[slow instrumental music playing]</i>

1:39:37.791 --> 1:39:39.791
<i>[music continues]</i>

1:40:38.208 --> 1:40:40.208
<i>[music continues]</i>

1:41:55.583 --> 1:41:57.583
<i>[gentle instrumental music playing]</i>
